quran[856]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  26,2,∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere …ìanngunde nden
  26,3,Belajo'o an a tampiniray hoore maa…óa kin fii …ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe
  26,4,Si Men Muuyii Men jippinay e ma…ì…ìe immorde ka kammu Aaya daa…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen √±alla ko …óe yankinanii…óe mo
  26,5,Arataa e ma…ì…ìe waaju immorde ka Hinnorante On fu…ó…óaangu si wanaa …ìe laatike …óuurii…ìe ngu
  26,6,Gom…óii …ìe fennii aroyay e ma…ì…ìe kabaruuji ko …ìe laatinoo ko…ìe jalkitano
  26,7,"Enee, …ìe yi'aali faade e leydi ndin, no foti hewde ko Men fu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone teddu…óo"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo On"
  26,10,"Ja≈ãto tuma nde Joomi maa…óa noddunoo Muusaa, …óum woni aru e yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  26,11,"Yim…ìe Fir'awna, kaa on hulataa"
  26,12,"O maaki: \"Joom am , min mi…óo huli wata …ìe fennam"
  26,13,"∆Åernde am nden …ìittoo hara …óemngal am ngal wellitaaki, awa Nulu Haaruuna"
  26,14,No woodani …ìe e dow am bakkaatu mi…óo huli fii wata …ìe waram
  26,15,"O Daali: \"Wanaa non, yahee onon …ói…óo, Men…óen wonndi e moo…óon ko Men he…óii…ìe"
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna wi'on: \"Menen dey ko men Nulaa…ìe Jooma winndere nden"
  26,17,∆äum woni accitu …ìi…ó…ìe Isra'iila …ìen wonndude e amen
  26,18,"O wi'i: \"Enee, men ne'aano ma ka amen …óoo hari ko a boobo, √±ii…ìu…óaa ka amen …óoo duu…ìi e ngurndam maa…óam"
  26,19,"Gollu…óaa gollal maa…óa ngal golluno…óaa ngal, an ko e yeddu…ìe …ìen jeya…óaa"
  26,20,"O maaki: \"Mi wa…óii …óum, ontuma hara min ko mi jeyaa…óo e majju…ìe …ìen"
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi hulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal O wa…óin mi jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,22,"∆äum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi …óum, fii a maccin…óinii …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nden"
  26,24,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaa…ìe"
  26,25,"O wi'ani …ìen wonu…ìe ban≈ãe makko: \"Enee; on he…óataako"
  26,26,"O maaki: \"Joomi moo…óon e Jooma baabiraa…ìe ardii…ìe …ìen"
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Pellet, Nulaa…óo moo…óon on Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon ko o feetu…óo"
  26,28,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma funnaange e hirnaange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike hakkiloo…ìe"
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Mi woondii si jogitike rewetee…óo tanaa am, mi wa…óete jeyaa…óo dummbaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,30,"O maaki: \"Enee, hay si mi addanii ma huunde …ìanngunde"
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Awa addu …óum, si tawii ko e goongu …ìen jeyaa…óaa"
  26,32,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande(ngoolwa) …ìannguba"
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaaroo…ìe …ìen"
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngun fee makko: \"Pellet, oo…óoo ko mbileejo heewu…óo ganndal"
  26,35,Himo faandii yaltinirgol on ka leydi moo…óon mbilewu makko ngun. Ko hun…óun yamir…óon
  26,36,"∆Åe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ca'e …óen moo…ìoo…ìe (mbile)"
  26,37,∆Åe addane kala mbileejo anndu…óo
  26,38,Mbilee…ìe …ìen moo…ìaa fii fodoore √±alaande anndaande
  26,39,"Yim…ìe …ìen wi'anaa: \"Taw si onon ko on moo…ìike(ndenndi)"
  26,40,"Belajo'o menen men jokkay mbilee…ìe …ìen, si …ìe laatike ko kam…ìe woni foolu…ìe …ìen"
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbilee…ìe …ìen arunoo; …ìe wi'ani Fir'awna: \"Enee, hara no woodani men njo…ìdi si tawii ko men woni foolu…ìe …ìen"
  26,42,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray ontuma on jeyaama e …ìa…ótinaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ìe: \"mbeddee, ko werloton kon"
  26,44,"∆Åe li…ìi …ìokkoy ma…ì…ìe koy e cawoy ma…ì…ìe kon, …ìe wi'i: \"Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko menen woni fooloo…ìe …ìen"
  26,45,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun, tawi kayru hindu mo…óa ko …ìe fefindii kon"
  26,46,Mbilee…ìe …ìen suuyi …ìe sujji
  26,47,"∆Åe wi'i : \"Men gom…óinii Jey…óo Winndere nden"
  26,48,Jey…óo Muusaa e Haaruuna
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, on gom…óinay mo, ko adii mi du≈ãanaade on? Pellet, ko kanko woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngun, kono aray anndon, mami ta∆¥u juu…óe moo…óon e koy…óe moo…óon [ta∆¥a] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fow moo…óon"
  26,50,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Tanaa alaa, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo"
  26,51,"Menen me…óen tam∆¥inii nde Joomi amen yawtani men goopi amen …óin,tawde men laatike adii…ìe gom…óinnde …ìen"
  26,52,"Men Wahayini faade e Muusaa: \"∆äum woni ro∆¥idu e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen. Pellet, onon ko on jokkitetee…ìe"
  26,53,Fir'awna nuli ka ca'e moo…ìoo…ìe
  26,54,"[O wi'i:] Pellet, …ìee ko …ìe mojobun pamarun"
  26,55,"Pellet, kam…ìe hi…ìe tikkinnde men"
  26,56,Enen non en fow ko en rentii…ìe
  26,57,Men yaltini …ìe immorde e gese e can…ói
  26,58,E ngaluuji e √±ii…ìirde teddunde
  26,59,"Ko wano nii, Men ronini …óum …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  26,60,∆Åe jokki…ìe ka pu…óal
  26,61,"Tuma nde jamaaji …óin …óin yi'ndirnoo, yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen wi'i: \"Enen en hewtoyte"
  26,62,"O maaki: \"∆äum wa…óataa, pellet, Joomi am no wonndi e am O fewnay lam"
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa, …óum woni piyir tuggordu maa…óa ndun maayo ngon, ngo seekii seekol kala seekol na foti e tulde mawnde"
  26,64,Men …ìanni ton heddii…ìe …ìen
  26,65,Men danndi Muusaa e wonndu…ìe e makko …ìen fow ma…ì…ìe
  26,66,Refti Men yooli heddii …ìe …ìen
  26,67,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,68,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,69,Janngan …ìe kumpital fii Ibraahiima
  26,70,Tuma nde o wi'annoo ben makko e yim…ìe makko …ìen; ko hon…óum rewoton
  26,71,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Me…óen rewude sanamuuji, men √±allay ufinanaade …ói"
  26,72,"O maaki: \"Yalli hi…ói nanana on, nde noddoton"
  26,73,Kaa hi…ói nafa on maa…óum …ói lorra on
  26,74,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko woni, men tawii baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen konii …ìe golliraynoo"
  26,75,"O maaki: \"Enee, on yi'ii kon ko wonu…óon e rewude"
  26,76,Onon e baabiraa…ìe moo…óon adinoo…ìe …ìen
  26,77,"Pellet, kam…ìe ko …ìe ay…ìe am, si wanaa Jooma winndire nden"
  26,78,"On Tagu…óo lam, ko Kanko fewnata lam"
  26,79,On ko Kanko √±amminta lam O yarnan-mi
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii, ko Kanko sellinta lam"
  26,81,E On waray…óo lam refti O wurnitan mi
  26,82,"On Mo mi tam∆¥inii kadi nde O yaafatoomi goopi am …óin √ëalnde [njo…ìdi] Diina kan"
  26,83,"Joomam, okkam Ganndal wattidaa mi e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen. @Corrected"
  26,84,Wa…óanaa lam …óemngal goongungal ka sakkitii…ìe …ìen
  26,85,Wa…óaa mi jeyaa…óo e ronoo…ìe Aljanna Neemaaji …óin
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaa…óo e majju…ìe …ìen"
  26,87,Wata A hersinoyam √ëalnde …ìe Immital
  26,88,√ëalnde nde jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe nafataa
  26,89,Si wanaa on ardu…óo ka Alla e …ìernde hisunde
  26,90,Aljanna on …ìatinanee huloo…ìe Alla …ìen
  26,91,Jahiim ngen fe√±√±inanee bew…ìe …ìen
  26,92,"∆Åe wi'nee: \"Honto woni ko laatino…óon kon hi…óon rewa"
  26,93,Gaanin Alla? Taw si …ói wallay on maa…óum …ói wallay hoore majji
  26,94,∆Åe hippee e nder magge kan…ìe e bew…ìe …ìen
  26,95,E konnuuji ibliisa …óin …ói fow majji
  26,96,∆Åe wi'i tawi kam…ìe hi…ìe wennjondira nder ton
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla, men woniino e nder majjere …ìanngunde"
  26,98,Tuma nde men fonnunoo on e Jooma winndere nden
  26,99,Majjinaali men si wonaa bon…ìe …ìen
  26,100,Alanaa men tefoo…ìe
  26,101,Wanaa kadi gi…óo √±allam…ìereejo(tigi tigi)
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men rutteede, men laatoo jeyaa…ìe e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,105,Yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen fenni Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,108,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,110,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,111,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gom…óinte, jaasu…ìe …ìen no jokkumaa"
  26,112,"O maaki: \"Ko hon…óum woni ganndal am e ko …ìe wonunoo e gollude"
  26,113,"Hasboore ma…ì…ìe nden fawaaki si wanaa e Joomi am, sinndo hi…óon so'aynoo"
  26,114,Min mi wonaali ra…óotoo…óo gom…óin…ìe …ìen
  26,115,Min mi wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo …ìanngu…óo
  26,116,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woondii si a accaali an Nuuhu, ma a laato sanne jeyaa…óo e rajmetee…ìe …ìen"
  26,117,"O maaki: \"Joom am, pellet, yim…ìe am …ìen …ìe fenni lam"
  26,118,"√ëaawu hakkunde am e ma…ì…ìe √±aawoore, danndaa mi e …ìen wonndu…ìe e am jeyaa…ìe e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  26,119,Men danndi mo e …ìen wonndu…ìe e makko ka nder laana ∆¥oltiika(loowaaka)
  26,120,"Refti Men yooli …ìaawo [ma…ì…ìe] heddii…ìe …ìen"
  26,121,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,122,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,123,Aadinkoo…ìe …ìen fenniino Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,124,"Tuma nde Huudu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,125,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,126,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,127,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,128,"Enee, on mahay maande e kala tulde hi…óon fija"
  26,129,"Jogito…óon ku…ìeeje a wi'ayma onon ko on luttintee…ìe [ka aduna]"
  26,130,"Si on jaggitii, janggiton ko ndunndarankoo…ìe"
  26,131,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,132,Hulee On …ìeydir…óo on ko anndu…óon
  26,133,O …ìeydiri on neemoraa…ói e …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe
  26,134,E gese e can…ói
  26,135,"[O maaki] min dey, mi…óo hulani on Lepte √ëalaande mawnde"
  26,136,"∆Åe wi'i: \"No fotana men ter, si a waajike maa…óum si a laataaki jeyaa…óo e waajotoo…ìe …ìen"
  26,137,"Pellet, …óum wonaali si wanaa jikku adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  26,138,Menen men wonaali leptoytee…ìe
  26,139,"∆Åe fenni mo, Men halki …ìe. Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,141,Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìen fenniino Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,143,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,144,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,145,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,146,"Enee, hara on accete e koo ko woni …óoo ko on hoolii…ìe"
  26,147,E nder gese e can…ói
  26,148,E remuruuji e tamarooje hara dukke majje ko …ìenndu…óum
  26,149,"Hi…óon lesa pelle …óen [wa…óon] cuu…ói ko on haawitii…ìe"
  26,150,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,151,Wata on …óofto yamaruyee fantinoo…ìe …ìen
  26,152,∆Åen bonnoo…ìe ka leydi hara …ìe mo∆¥∆¥intaa
  26,153,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo mbilaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,154,"An a wonaali si wanaa …ìanndunke yeru amen, awa addu Aaya, si tawii a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  26,155,"O maaki: \"Mbaa…óoo ko naaqawa, no woodani mba yaramnde, no woodani on onon kadi yaramnde √±alaande anndaande"
  26,156,"Wata on memir mba ko boni, sakko nannga on Lepte √ëalnde Mawnde"
  26,157,"∆Åe mborii mba, …ìe wonti nimsu…ìe"
  26,158,"Lepte …óen nanngi …ìe. Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,159,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,160,Yim…ìe Luutu …ìen fenni Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,161,"Tuma nde Luutu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,162,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,163,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,164,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,165,"Enee, on aray wor…ìe …ìen immorde e winndere nden"
  26,166,"∆äalon ko Joomi moo…óon tagani on kon immorde e sonnaa…ìe moo…óon? Ko woni, onon ko on yim…ìe jaggitu…ìe"
  26,167,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men woondii si a accaali an Luutu, ma a laato sanne jeyaa…óo e yaltitee…ìe …ìen"
  26,168,"O maaki: \"Min dey, mi…óo jeyaa e a√±u…ìe …ìen golle moo…óon …óen"
  26,169,"Jooma, danndam min e …ìeynguure am nden kon ko …ìe gollata"
  26,170,"Men danndi mo e …ìeynguure makko nden, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe"
  26,171,Si wonaa jiidiraare(nayeejo debbo) nden ka halkaa…ìe …ìen
  26,172,Refti Men o∆¥∆¥i heddii …ìe …ìen
  26,173,"Men to…ìini e dow ma…ì…ìe to…ìo, bonii to…ìo jertinaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,174,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,175,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,176,Yim…ìe fitaare(sutu) nden fenniino Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  26,177,"Tuma nde Su'aybu wi'annoo …ìe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,178,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,179,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,180,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,181,"Humnee …ìetu ngun, wata on laato jeyaa…ìe e uytoo…ìe …ìen"
  26,182,Manndikiree(peesre) manndikir…óe feewu…óe …óen
  26,183,"Wata on ustan yim…ìe …ìen piiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, wata on lancito ka leydi hara ko on bonnoo…ìe"
  26,184,"Hulee On Tagu…óo on, o tagu adinoongu ngun"
  26,185,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo mbil…óaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,186,"An a wonaali si wanaa …ìanndunke yeru amen, tawde me…óen jikkumaa ko a jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  26,188,"O maaki: \"Ko Joomi am woni Anndu…óo ko golloton kon"
  26,189,"∆Åe fenni mo, nanngi …ìe Lepte √±alaande …óowdiinde nden. Pellet, …óen laatino Lepte √±alaande mawnde"
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ìur…ìe heewu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe"
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Jooma winndere nden"
  26,193,Jippinii nde Ruuhu hoolaa…óo on
  26,194,Ka …ìernde maa…óa fii yo a laato jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ìe …ìen
  26,195,E …óemngal Aarabu …ìanngungal
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hinde ka …óeri aran…ìe …ìen"
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki …ìe Maande, nde tawata anndiino nde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila anndu…ìe …ìen"
  26,198,Sinndo Men jippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyankoo…ìe …ìen
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow ma…ì…ìe, …ìe laatotaako gom…óin…ìe nde"
  26,200,Ko wano nii Men naadiri …óum e …ìer…óe bon…ìe …ìen
  26,201,"∆Åe gom…óintaa nde, haa …ìe yi'a Lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  26,202,"∆äe ara e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee, hara …ìe so'aa"
  26,203,"Sakko …ìe wi'a: \"Taw si ko men nennantee…ìe"
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte Amen …óen …ìe he√±orta"
  26,205,A tinii si Men dakmitii …ìe duu…ìi
  26,206,Refti ari e ma…ì…ìe kon ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe fodee
  26,207,Nafaali …ìe ko …ìe laatinoo kon hi…ìe dakmitoo
  26,208,"Men halkaali saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde jertinoo…ìe"
  26,209,"[∆äum] ko waaju, Men laataaki too√±oo…ìe"
  26,210,Wanaa seytanuuji …óin jippini nde
  26,211,"[∆äum] haananaa…ói, …ói hattantaake kadi"
  26,212,"Pellet, kannji ko …ói follatee…ói gaayi he…óagol ngol"
