  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo …ìeynguure makko nden: \"Min dey, mi haynike yiite, aray mi addana on ka nge woni …óon kumpital maa…óum mi addana on docotal hu…ì…ìungal, bela jo'o onon on iwloto"
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge, o noddaa: ∆äum woni barkinaama on won…óo ka yiite e …ìen wonu…ìe ban≈ãe magge, e Senayee wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden"
  27,9,"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla Teddu…óo √ëee√±u…óo On"
  27,10,"Li…ìu tuggordu maa…óa ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hindu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboddi, o hucciti ko o dogu…óo o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: \"Wata a hulu, Min dey Nulaa…ìe …ìen hulataa ka Am"
  27,11,"Si wanaa on too√±u…óo, refti o lontini ko mo∆¥∆¥i …ìaawo bone …óen. Pellet, Min ko Mi Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  27,12,"Naadu junngo maa…óa ngon ka jiiba maa…óa, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, […óum no jeyaa] e nder Aayeeje jeenay nulaa…óe e Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen, pellet, kam…ìe …ìe laatike yim…ìe faasiqii…ìe"
  27,13,"Tuma nde arunoo e ma…ì…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen ko yi'etee…óe, …ìe wi'i: \"∆äu'um, ko mbilewu …ìanngungu"
  27,14,"∆Åe yeddi [Aayeeje …óen], tawi wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin no yananaa fii majje, too√±e e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane fennu…ìe …ìen"
  27,15,"Gom…óii Men okkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal …ìe maaki: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On …ìurnu…óo men e dow …óuu…óu…ìe immorde e jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, men anndinaama haala colli …óin, men okkaama immorde e kala huunde, Pellet, …óum…óoo ko …óum woni …ìural …ìanngungal"
  27,17,"Sulaymaana moo…ìanaa koneeli makko …óin immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yim…ìe e ka colli, kam…ìe ko …ìe yu…ì…ìinaa…ìe"
  27,18,"Haa nde …ìe arunoo e aynde korndolli …óin, korndolil wi'i: \"Ko onon yo korndolli, naatee ka ko…óan…ói moo…óon, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'un …óin muncu on, hara kam…ìe …ìe so'aa"
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jalu…óo immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: \"Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maa…óa mo neemin…óaa e dow am on, e jibibin…ìe lam …ìen, e nde mi gollata ko mo∆¥∆¥i weltoraa …óum, naadaami ka Yurmeende Maa…óa wonndude e jeyaa…ìe Maa…óa mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  27,20,"O ∆¥ewtii colli …óin, o maaki: \"Ko he…ìi lam, mi yi'aali Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jeyaandu e wirnii…ói …óin"
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte sa…ótu…óe maa…óum maa mi hirsandu sanne, maa…óum ndu addana lam hujja …ìanngu…óo"
  27,22,"Ndu √±ii…ìe ko wo…ó…óaa, ndu wi'i: \"Mi hu…ìindike ko a hu…ìindaaki …óum, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal"
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii …ìe himo okkaa immorde e kala huunde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde"
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen hi…ìe sujjana naange ngen gaanin Alla; Seytaane no cu…óani…ìe golle ma…ì…ìe …óen o faddii …ìe gaayi Laawol ngol, kam…ìe …ìe feewataa"
  27,25,Ko ha…óata …ìe sujjana Alla On yaltinoowo ko suu…óii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi hiMo Anndi ko suu…óoton e ko fe√±inton
  27,26,"Alla, Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  27,27,"O maaki: \"Aray men ndaara si a goongu, maa…óum si laati jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  27,28,"Yahidu e nduu talkuru am werlo…óaa ndu ka ma…ì…ìe, refti huccaa …ìe ndaaraa ko hon…óum …ìe ruttata"
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, min dey werlaama ka am talkuru teddundu"
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: \"Innde Alla Huu…ìu…óo Yurmeende Heerii…óo Yurmeende On"
  27,31,"Wata on townitano lam, aree e am ko jebbilii…ìe"
  27,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, wa…ótee lam e feere e …óee fiyaake am, mi laataaki ta∆¥oowo fiyaake haa tawde…óon e am"
  27,33,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare sa…ótu…óe, fiyaake …óen ko ka maa…óa woni, ndaaru ko hon…óum yamirtaa"
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: \"Pellet, lam…ìe …ìen si …ìe naatii e saare …ìe bonnay nde, …ìe wa…óa teddu…ìe mayre …ìen hoy…ìe, ko wanonii …ìe gollirta"
  27,35,"Awa min, mi nulay e ma…ì…ìe neldaari, mi ndaara ko hon…óum nulaa…ìe …ìen ruttodata"
  27,36,"Tuma nde …ìe arunoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: \"Enee, on …ìeydiray lam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkin mi, no …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hi…óon farnora neldaari moo…óon ndin"
  27,37,"Rutto ka ma…ì…ìe, mamen addana …ìe koneeli …ói …ìe maraa feere muu…óum, mamen yaltin …ìe ton ko …ìe jaasu…ìe hara kam…ìe ko hoy…ìe"
  27,38,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, ko hommbo e moo…óon addanta lam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii …ìe arude ka am ko …ìe jebbilii…ìe"
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: \"Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maa…óa nden, e pellet, min e dow …óum ko mi dolnu…óo hoolaa…óo"
  27,40,"On mo woni ka muu…óum ganndal immorde ka Deftere wi'i: \"Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndar…óe maa…óa …óen ruttotoo e maa…óa\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde √±ii…ìunde ka makko, o maaki: \"∆äum …óoo, ko immorde e ∆Åural Joomi am, fii yo O ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [Mo] maa…óum si mi yedday [Mo], kala jarnu…óo anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yeddu…óo kadi pellet, Joomi am ko O Galo Teddu…óo"
  27,41,"O maaki: \"Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditay, kaa o laatoto jeyaa…óo e …ìen …ìe annditataa"
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arunoo, [o] wi'aa: \"Enee, ko nii jullere maa…óa nden wa'i?\" O wi'i: \"Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii\". Men okkaama ganndal ko adii mo, men laatii jebbilii…ìe"
  27,43,"Faddii mo, …óum ko o laatinoo himo rewa gaanin Alla, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe yeddu…ìe"
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: \"Naatu ka hu…ìeere\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o √±ori dense (korle)makko …óen. [Sulaymaana] maaki: \"Pellet, ndee ko hu…ìeere new…óiniraande ndaaror…óe\". [Debbo on] wi'i: \"Jooma, min dey mi too√±ii wonkii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wonndude e Sulaymaana"
  27,45,"Gom…óii Men Nulii faade e Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìen musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on Saalihu, …óum woni rewee Alla. Tawi kam…ìe ko …ìe feddeeji …ói…ói hi…ìe wennjondira"
  27,46,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, ko fii hon…óun he√±ornton bone …óen ko adii mo∆¥∆¥ere nden?\" \"Ko ha…ói insinanino Alla bela jo'o onon on yurminoyte"
  27,47,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men kiitinorii ma e …ìen wonndu…ìe e maa…óa\". O maaki: \"kiite moo…óon on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yim…ìe fitnetee…ìe\" @Corrected"
  27,48,Laatinoke ka saare ton wor…ìe njeenayo hi…ìe bonna ka leydi …ìe mo∆¥∆¥intaa
  27,49,"∆Åe wi'i: ∆Åe woondirii Alla, ma men waalanan mo ka suudu kanko e …ìeynguure makko nden refti ma men wi'an jey…ìe mo …ìen; men tawaaka warugol yim…ìe makko …ìen, e pellet, menen ko men goongu…ìe\". @Corrected"
  27,50,"∆Åe hodi hodoore Menen kadi Men fewji fewjoore, tawi kam…ìe …ìe so'ataa"
