  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo fewnata on ka ni…ìe njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni …óin wewliniray…ói fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla? Alla Toowii gaayi ko …ìe sirkata kon. @Corrected"
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni fu…ó…óu…óo tagu ngun refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla? Maaku: \"Addee daliili moo…óon on si tawii ko on goongu…ìe"
  27,65,"Maaku: \"Anndaa ko wirnii kon …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa Alla. ∆Åe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma …ìe immintinoytee"
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal ma…ì…ìe ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kam…ìe hi…ìe e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kam…ìe ko …ìe wumu…ìe fii …óum"
  27,67,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe wi'i: \" Enee, hay si men laatike mbullaari e baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen kadi, e hara menen ko men yaltinoytee…ìe"
  27,68,"Gom…óii men fodanooma …óum menen e baabiraa…ìe amen ko adii, …óum wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinoo…ìe"
  27,69,"Maaku : \"Yehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bon…ìe …ìen laatornoo"
  27,70,"Wata a suno fii ma…ì…ìe, wata a laato e …ìitteende immorde e ko …ìe fewjata kon"
  27,71,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  27,72,"Maaku: \"No tijjaa nde tawata …ìadanike on yoga e kon ko …óa…ì…ìu…óon yaccinaneede"
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko O Jom ∆Åural e dow yim…ìe …ìen, kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe …ìe jarnataa [Alla]"
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa hiMo Anndi ko …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen soomi e ko …óe fe√±√±inta kon"
  27,75,"Alaa e wirniikun ka kammu e ka leydi si wanaa [fii makkun] no e nder Deftere …ìanngunde"
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hinde filloo e dow …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen fii huunde nde …ìe …ìuri luutondirde nden e fii muu…óum"
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonannde gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa O √±aawiray hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √ëaawoore Makko ngal, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Anndu…óo"
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an hi…óa e hoore Goonga …ìannguka kan"
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa may…ìe …ìen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ìe …ìen noddaandu ndun si …ìe …óuurnike …ìe huccitii"
  27,81,An a wonaali fewnoowo bum…ìe …ìen e gaayi majjere ma…ì…ìe nden. A nanintaa si wanaa …ìen gom…óin…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ìe ko …ìe jebbilii…ìe
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow ma…ì…ìe, Men yaltinana …ìe daabewa immorde ka leydi himba haalana …ìe wonnde yim…ìe …ìen laatike …ìe yananaaka Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  27,83,E √±alnde Men moo…ìoyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaa…ìe e …ìen fennoo…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ìe hi…ìe soggee
  27,84,"Haa si …ìe arii, O Daala: \"Eyoo, on fenniino Aayeeje Am …óen, hara on hu…ìindoraali …ói ganndal. Kaa ko hon…óum won…óon e gollude"
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e ma…ì…ìe sabu ko …ìe too√±i kon, kam…ìe …ìe wowlataa"
  27,86,"Enee, hara …ìe yi'aali, Menen Men wa…óii jemma on fii yo …ìe dee∆¥u e maako, e √±alorma on yi'ir…óo? Pellet, wonii e …óum Aayeeje wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe …ìen"
  27,87,"E √ëalnde wuttoytee ka alaadu, …óen∆¥oo …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e …ìen wonu…ìe ka leydi, si wanaa …ìen …ìe Alla muuyi, gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe aray e Makko hara ko …ìe hoykinii…ìe"
  27,88,"Hi…óa tina pelle …óen, sikka ko …óe fenndii…óe, hara le kannje hi…óe wuloo wulagol duule …óen, …óum ko kuugal Alla, On ≈ãar…óin…óo kala huunde, pellet, Kanko ko O Humpitii…óo ko golloton kon"
  27,89,"Mo ardii e mo∆¥∆¥ere nden haray no woodani mo ko …ìuri nde mo∆¥∆¥ude, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe hoolii…ìe immorde e …óen∆¥ere nden √ëalnde"
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone …óen, geece ma…ì…ìe …óen hippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yo…ìete si wanaa kon ko laatino…óon hi…óon golla"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi Rewu Jooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini …óum, no woodani Mo kala huunde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jeyaa…óo e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare nden, mo feewii haray ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ìe …ìen"
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje Makko …óen anndon …óe\". Joomi maa…óa wonaali welsindii…óo gaay e kon ko golloton"
  28,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  28,2,∆äee ko Aayeeje Deftere …ìanngunde nden
  28,3,"Me…óen janngira e maa…óa hoore goonga, kumpital Muusaa e Fir'awna, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna townitino ka leydi; o wa…ói yim…ìe mayri ndin pecce-pecce: himo lo'ina fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe, o hirsa …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe wor…ìe …ìen o acca rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen. Pellet, ko e bonnoo…ìe …ìen o jeyanoo"
  28,5,"Me…óen faandinoo mo∆¥∆¥agol e lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen ka leydi; Men wa…óa …ìe koohoo…ìe, Men wa…óa …ìe kadi ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,6,"Men hu…ìindina …ìe e leydi ndin, Men holla Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli ma…ì…ìe …óin, kon ko …ìe hulaynoo"
  28,7,"Men wahayini e yumma Muusaa, wonnde: \"Muynin mo\". Si a hulanoyii mo, ko yo a bugoyo mo ka maayo. Wata a hulu, wata a suno; pellet, Men ruttay mo ka maa…óa, Men wa…óoya mo gooto e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,8,"Yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen hocci mo, fii yo laatano …ìe ga√±o e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe laatino woopu…ìe"
  28,9,"Debbo Fir'awna on wi'i: \"(Kun entum ko) …ìuu…ìeendi gite am e an kadi! Wata on waru mo, hino gasa ka o nafata en, maa jogitoren mo …ìi…ó…óo\". Hari …ìe so'aani"
  28,10,"∆Åernde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewunde. Haa o e…ì…ìi fe√±√±inde fii makko, si wanaano Men tabintinnde …ìernde makko nden, fii yo o laato e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  28,11,"[Yumma Muusaa] wi'ani banndiraawo makko on: \"Jokkitu mo\"; o haynii mo ka deestii, hari …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  28,12,"Men harminani mo ko adii, (en…ói) muynir…ói …óin, (banndiraawo makko on) wi'i: \"On accay mi tinndinay on fii yim…ìe suudu, …ìe ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laa…ìanay …ìe mo"
  28,13,"Men rutti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo …ìernde makko …ìuu…ìu, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe anndaa"
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Men okki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, fewndo welsindaare yim…ìe mayre; o tawi wor…ìe …ói…óo no ha…ìa ton: go…ó…óo on ko jeyaa…óo e le√±ol makko, oya on ko jeyaa…óo e ay…ìe makko …ìen. Jeyaa…óo e le√±ol makko ngol …óa…ì…ìiri faabo e hoore jeyaa…óo e ga√±o makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum …óoo, ko jeyaa…óum e kuu…óe seytaane. Pellet, ko o ga√±o, majjinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  28,16,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi too√±ii hoore-am; haforanam.\" O haforani mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  28,17,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, sabu ko neemin…óaa kon e am, mi wontataa ballo bom…ìe …ìen"
  28,18,"O wonti hul…óo ka saare, himo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornoo…óo mo on hanki, hino faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: \"Pellet, ko a bew…óo …ìanngu…óo"
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol taw…óo on ko ga√±o ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, a faala warugol lam, wano ittirno…óaa wonkii non hanki? A faandaaki, si wanaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ìuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii warugol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jeyaa…óo e laa…ìanoo…ìe ma"
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o hulu…óo, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: \"Joomi am, dan…óndam e yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,22,"Nde o fewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: \"Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka …ìunndu Madyana, o tawi …óon dental yim…ìe, hi…ìe yarna [daabeeji ma…ì…ìe], o tawi gaanin ma…ì…ìe, rew…ìe …ói…óo, no sogga [dammi ma…ì…ìe], o maaki: \"Ko hon…óum habbi-…óon?\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Men yarnataa haa aynoo…ìe …ìen deestoo, baaba amen, ko maw…óo nayeejo"
  28,24,"O yarnani …ìe [dammi …óin], refti o huccitiri ka …óowdi, o maaki: \"Joomi am, min ko jippin…óaa e am woo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, ko mi hatonji…óo"
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen ari e makko, himo yahra hersa, o wi'i: \"Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yo…ìe njo…ìdi kon ko yarnan-…óaa men\". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [maw…óo] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: \"Wata a hulu, a da…óii yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen wi'i: \"∆≥ettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mo ∆¥ettataa golle, ko doolnu…óo hoolnii…óo"
  28,27,"[Maw…óo] on maaki: \"Mi…óo yi…ói resingol ma gooto e jiw…ìe am …ìen …óoo …ói…óo, e hoore yo a golla-nam duu…ìi jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka sa…ótinannde ma. A taway lam, si Alla ja…ìii, ko e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen mi jeyaa"
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"∆äum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji …ói…ói, …ói mi hunni, haray …ìi…óteede alanaa e lam. En wa…óii Alla fawtii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon"
  28,29,"Nde Muusaa timminnoo happu ngun, o yahdi e …ìeydnuure makko, o haynii yiite ka senngo (fello) Tuuri, o maaki …ìeunguure makko nden: \"Wonee …óoo, min mi haynike yiite. Belajo'o mi addana on e magge kumpital maa te'annde(docotal) yiite ngen, belajo'o iwloron"
  28,30,"Nde o hewtunoo nge, o noddiraa ka fonngo √±aamo aynde, ka tummbere barkinaande, ka (takko) lekki, wonnde: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Ko Min woni Alla, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  28,31,"Kadi: \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\"; nde o tinunoo hindu dillira wa mboddi,o huccitiri dogudu, o ye∆¥∆¥itaaki. [O noddaa]: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Artu, wata a hulu; ko a jeyaa…óo e hoolii…ìe …ìen"
  28,32,"Naadu juungo maa ngon ka jayba maa, ngo yaltay ranewo, ko aldaa e √±awu. Bakaa e maa…óa, juu…óe maa …óen, fii kulol ngol. ∆äin ko hujjaaji …ói…ói, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e Fir'awna e dental mun, pellet, …ìen laatike yim…ìe faasiqii…ìe"
  28,33,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi ittiino wonkii e ma…ì…ìe, mi…óo huli nde …ìe warata lam"
  28,34,"Ko musi…ó…óo am on Haaruuna, …ìuri lam laa…ìude …óemngal. Immindin-mo e am, ko wallitoo lam, goonginan-mi; mi…óo huli nde …ìe fennata lam"
  28,35,"[Alla] daali: \"Men semmbiniray tere maa …óen, musi…ó…óo maa on, Men wa…óana on hujja (e cemmbe); …ìe hewtirtaa on …ói…óo, sabu Aayeeje Amen …óe [Men nuli e] mo'on, e …ìen jokku…ìe on foolu…ìe"
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa ardunoo e ma…ì…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen …ìanngu…óe, …ìe wi'i: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu fefindaangu. Men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude on ardu…óo e peewal, immorde ka Makko, e on mo battane mo∆¥∆¥e woodani ka laakara. Pellet, O malnataa too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Ko onon dental, mi anndanaa on rewetee…óo, si wanaa min. Ko an yo Haamaana, hu…ì…ìinanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa lam hu…ìeere toowunde, no gasa ka mi ∆¥ellitoo e Rewetee…óo Muusaa On; tawde mi…óo sikki mo e fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kanko e koneeli makko …óin, ko aldaa e goonga. ∆Åe sikki wonde …ìe ruttitetaako ka Amen"
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kanko e koneeli makko …óin, Men bugii …ìe ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane too√±u…ìe …ìen wa'unoo"
  28,41,"Men wa…ói …ìe ardii…ìe, noddoo …ìe e Yiite. √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe walletaake"
  28,42,"Men jokkintiniri …ìe ka aduna …óoo, kuddi. √ëalnde Darngal, ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe e wo…ó…óintinoytee…ìe [e yurmeende Alla]"
  28,43,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, …ìaawo nde Men halkunoo gire arane …óen, ko nde ndayginorde yim…ìe …ìen, e peewal e yurmeende. Belajo'o, …ìe waajitoray"
  28,44,"A tawanooka ka senngo hiirnaange, fewndo Men wahyinnoo e Muusaa yamiroore nden, a jeyanooka kadi e seedii…ìe …ìen"
  28,45,"Kono Menen woni tagu…ìe gire, duu…ìi ma…ì…ìe juuti. A ho…óaano kadi e yim…ìe Madyana …ìen, hi…óa janngana …ìe Aayeeje Amen; ko Menen woni nul…ìe"
  28,46,"A tawanooka ka senngo Fello Tuuri, fewndo Men noddunoo; ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa [woni ko Men nulir-maa], fii no jertiniraa yim…ìe, …ìe reentinoowo araali e ma…ì…ìe, ado maa…óa, belajo'o, …ìe waajitoto"
  28,47,"Si wanaano fii yo lepte yanir e ma…ì…ìe, sabu ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe ardini, …ìe wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko ha…óno imminaa Nulaa…óo e amen? Men jokka nun Aayeeje Maa …óen, men jeyee e gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  28,48,"Nde o addirannoo…ìe goonga kan, immorde ka Amen, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko ha…óno o okkee yeru ko Muusaa okkanoo kon?\" Kere …ìe yeddaano ko Muusaa okkanoo kon ko adii? ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko mbileeji …ói…ói, …ói no wallindira!\" ∆Åe wi'i kadi: \"Ko men yeddu…ìe fow e mun"
  28,49,"Maaku: \"Addee Deftere immorde ka Alla, hara hinde …ìuri …óee …ói…ói feewude, mi jokkaynde, si on laatike goongun…ìe"
  28,50,"Si …ìe jaabaaki ma, anndu ko mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe …ìe jokkata. Ko hommbo …ìuri majjude …ìuri on jokkir…óo mbelee…óe mun, ko aldaa e peewal immorde ka Alla? Pellet, Alla fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  28,51,"Gom…óii Men hewtinii …ìe Konngol ngol, belajo'o, …ìe waajitora"
  28,52,"∆Åen …ìe Men rokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko …ìe gom…óim…ìe nde"
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet men woniino jebbilii…ìe, ado mayre"
  28,54,"∆Åen …óon, …ìe jonniroyte njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, laabi …ói…ói, sabu ko …ìe mu√±inoo kon, hi…ìe du√±iraynoo mo∆¥∆¥ere nden, bone on, e huunde nde Men arsiki …ìe nden, hi…ìe nafqa"
  28,55,"Si …ìe nanii meerente, …ìe …óuurnoo e …óum, …ìe wi'a: \"Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Men …óa…ì…ìataa wonndugol e majju…ìe …ìen"
  28,56,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), a fewnataa mo yi…óu…óaa; kono Alla no fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko …ìuri anndude feewu…ìe …ìen"
  28,57,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Si men jokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen\". E Men ho…óiniraali …ìe e nokku horminaa…óo, hoolnii…óo, mo dim…óe noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  28,58,"∆äuu…óii ko Men hakli, e yim…ìe ca'e, bewrunoo…ìe nguuree mun, e hino non galleeji ma…ì…ìe …óin, ho…óiraaka …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa see…óa. Men laatii wonnde ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali wonde halkoowo yim…ìe ca'e, haa O immina e lenyol ma…ì…ìe…óen, Nulaa…óo, ko janngana …ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Men siforaali kadi halkugol yim…ìe ca'e, si wanaa hara yim…ìe majje ko too√±u…ìe"
  28,60,"Kala ko okka…óon e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna e cu…óaari mun; ko ko woni ka Alla kon, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, woni kadi ko luttata. E on haqqiltaa"
  28,61,"E ko on mo Men fodi fodaari mo∆¥∆¥uri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Men dakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kanko on, √ëalnde Darngal, ko e tawnetee…ìe (ka Yiite) …ìen o jeyaa"
  28,62,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kafidaa…ói am, …óin …ói aa∆¥orayno…óon woni"
  28,63,"∆Åen …ìe Konngol jojji e mu'un wi'a: \"Joomi amen, ko …ìee woni ko men bewinnoo. Men bewinirno …ìe, wano men bewirnoo. Men da…óndinike e Maa…óa. Wanaa menen …ìe rewaynoo"
  28,64,"[∆Åe] wi'anee: \"Noddee non kafidaa…ói mon …óin\". ∆Åe nodda …ói, kono …ói jaabotaako …ìe. ∆Åe yi'a lepte …óen, (…ìe yeloo) sinno hara …ìe feewuno"
  28,65,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, o wi'a: \"Ko hon…óum jaabino…óon Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,66,"Lamitor…ói …óin wumi…óana …ìe nden √±alnde, …ìe lamndondirtaa"
  28,67,"Si ko tuubu…óo, o gom…óini, o golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaa…ìe …ìen"
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko O muuyi, O su…ìoo; su…ìagol alanaa …ìe. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkata"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen suu…óata, e kon ko …ìe fe√±√±inta"
  28,70,"Ko Kanko Alla woni, Mo rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko Kanko yettoore woodani aduna e laakara. Hino woodani Mo √±aawoore nden. Ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  28,71,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla wa…óiranii on jemma on, duumii…óo haa √ëalnde Darngal, ko rewetee…óo hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa"
  28,72,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla wa…óiranii on √±alorma on, duumii…óo haa √ëalnde Darngal, ko rewetee…óo hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo dee∆¥oton e mun? E on yi'ataa"
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O wa…óiranii on jemma e √±alorma; fii no dee∆¥iron e (jemma) on, e no …óa…ì…ìiron ( e √±alorma on), …ìural Makko, e no belajo'o yettiron [Mo]"
  28,74,"√ëalnde O noddoyta …ìe, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kadidaa…ói(renndidii…ói) am, …óin …óin aa∆¥orayno…óon woni"
  28,75,"Men …óoofi e kala mofte, seedotoo…óo, Men wi'a: \"Addee hujjaajji mon …óin\". ∆Åe anndi wonnde goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko …ìe fefindotonoo kon majjitora …ìe"
  28,76,"Pellet,Qaaruuna ko e yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen jeyanoo,kono o bewi e ma…ì…ìe.Men okki mo ngaluuji taway-…ói soktir…óe mun,no teddana jamaa doolnu…óo.Nde yim…ìe makko …ìen,wi'anno mo:Wata a weltor townitaare.Pellet Alla yi…óaa weltortoo…ìe toownitaare"
  28,77,"∆äa…ì…ìir ko Alla okku-maa kon, galle laakare …óen. Wata a yejjitu ge…ìal maa ngal aduna. Mo∆¥∆¥ir no Alla mo∆¥∆¥orii non e maa…óa. Wata a …óa…ì…ìu bonnugol ka leydi. Anndu pellet, Alla yi…óaa bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,78,"O wi'i: \"Ko mi okkiraa …óum, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii\". E o anndaa wonnde gom…óii Alla halkiino gire, adii…ìe mo, …ìur…ìe doole, …ìuri mo …óuu…óude jawle? ∆Åe lamndoytaake fii junuubi ma…ì…ìe, kam…ìe bom…ìe …ìen"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yim…ìe makko …ìen, cu…óaari makko ndin. Yi…óu…ìe nguurndam aduna …ìen wi'i: \"Hara nun men he…ìayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. Kanko on, pellet, ko o jom-ge…ìal mawnungal"
  28,80,"Okkaa…ìe ganndal …ìen kan wi'i: \"Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on gom…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i\". Kono hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  28,81,"Men mutindini mo e galle makko …óen, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko faaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano faabotoo…óo hoore-mun"
  28,82,"∆Åen yelinoo…ìe nokku makko on hanki mun, …ìe wa…óti wiide: \"Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O …ìi…ótinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wanaa Alla mo∆¥∆¥inoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  28,83,"∆äen galle laakara, Men wa…óanii …óe …ìen …ìe yi…óaa townitaare ka leydi, wanaa kadi bonnugol. Battane mo∆¥∆¥e …óen, ko fii gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  28,84,"Kala ardu…óo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, hino woodani mo ko …ìuri nde mo∆¥∆¥ude; kala kadi ardu…óo e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwu…ìe bon…ói …óin yo…ìetaake, si wanaa ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon"
  28,85,"Pellet, jippin…óo Alqur'aana on e maa…óa, ko ruttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: \"Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude ardu…óo e peewal, e won…óo e majjere …ìanngunde"
  28,86,"A wonaano tam∆¥ininoo…óo jippineede Deftere nden e maa…óa. Si wanaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wata wonu muk, walloowo heefer…ìe …ìen"
  28,87,"wata …ìe falo ma kadi e Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ìaawo …óe jippineede e maa…óa. Noddu (yim…ìe …ìen) faade e Joomi maa, wata a wonu muk, jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  28,88,"Wata a rewudu e Alla, rewetee…óo goo. Rewetee…óo goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Huunde fow re'ay, si wanaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko Kanko woodani √±aawugol; ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon. @Corrected"
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  29,2,"E yim…ìe …ìen sikku …ìe accirte nii, fii …ìe wi'ii: \"Men gom…óinii!\" Hara …ìe fitninaaka"
  29,3,"Gom…óii, Men fitninii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe. Maa Alla fe√±√±in, fii goongu…ìe …ìen, maa O fe√±√±in kadi, fii fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,4,"Kaa huuwu…ìe bon…ói …ìen sikku, wonnde …ìe laawoto Men? ko …ìe √±aawata kon bonii"
  29,5,"Kala taw…óo himo jortii hawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  29,6,"Kala kadi tii…ónii…óo, ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko yonndinii…óo e tageefo ngon"
  29,7,"∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men momtan …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, Men yo…ìitra …ìe, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  29,8,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on, mo∆¥∆¥ugol e maw…ìe makko …ìen. Si …ìe doolii maa fii sirkangol Lam, ko a alanaa …óum ganndal, wata a …óofto …ìe ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko gollayno…óon"
  29,9,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men wa…ótidu…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,10,"Hino e jim…ìe …ìen, wi'oowo: \"Men gom…óinii Alla\"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o wa…óay lorra yim…ìe …ìen, wano lepte Alla …óen. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ìe wi'ay: \"Me…óen wondunoo e mo'on!\" Kere wanaa Alla …ìuri anndude ko woni e …ìer…óe tageefo ngon"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ma O fe√±√±ina kadi fii naafiqii…ìe …ìen"
  29,12,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ani gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon …óin\". Kono …ìe wonaali fawtotoo…ìe hay huunde e goopi ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko …ìe fenoo…ìe"
  29,13,"Kono maa …ìe fawtoo fii teddeendi junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, e teddeendi goo, wonndude e teddeendi ma…ì…ìe ndin. Ko maa …ìe lamndoyee, √ëalnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko …ìe fefindotonoo"
  29,14,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o √±ii…ìi hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, duu…ìi ujunere, ≈ãakku…óum duu…ìi cappan…óe jowi. Waame on nanngi …ìe, hari ko …ìe too√±u…ìe"
  29,15,"Men da…óndi mo, kanko e yim…ìe laana kan; Men wa…ói ka kaawisa tageefo ngon"
  29,16,"(Janto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Rewee Alla, hulon Mo; ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, si woni hi…óon anndi"
  29,17,"Anndee ko reweton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, hi…óon ta∆¥a fenaande. Pellet, …óin …ói rewoton gaanin Alla, …ói waawaa on arsikude; …óa…ì…ìiree arsike on ka Alla, rewon Mo, yetton Mo. Ko ka Makko woni ruttete…óon"
  29,18,"Si on fennii, haray mofte adinoo…ìe kadi fenniino (Nulaa…ìe mun). Alaa ko fawii e Nulaa…óo on, si wanaa yottingol …ìannginngol"
  29,19,"E …ìee yi'aali no Alla fu…ó…óorta tagu ngun, refti O ruttay ngu? Pellet, …óum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  29,20,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O fu…ó…óori tagu ngun. Refti Alla taga tagu sakkitoru ngun. Pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  29,21,"Himo lepte mo O muuyani, O yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotoo…ìe ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on gaanin Alla, woni gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  29,23,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Alla …óen, e hawroygol e Makko ngol, …ìen ta∆¥ike e yurmeende Am, …ìen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe"
  29,24,"Jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Waree mo, maa sunnon mo\". Kono Alla da…óndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óim…ìe"
  29,25,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yi…óindiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, √ëalnde Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi hu…óo yoga, hara non, jaa∆¥orde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara walloo…ìe alanaa on"
  29,26,"Luutu gom…óini mo. O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,27,"Men ye…ói mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Men wa…ói e geyngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Men okki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,28,"(Janto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen : \" E on aray e pankare, …óe gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun"
  29,29,"E on aray yottagol e wor…ìe …ìen? palo…óon kadi e laawol? Huuwon ko mbatirdu mon ko a√±inii?\" Kono jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Addan men lepte Alla …óen, si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  29,30,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, wallam e hoore yim…ìe bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ìe wi\"i: \"Menen, ko men halkoo…ìee yim…ìe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ìe mayre laatike too√±oo…ìe"
  29,32,"O maaki: \"Kono Luutu no ton!\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko menen …ìuri anndude fii won…ìe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ìe …ìen"
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen hewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ì…ìe, …ìernde makko …ìi…ótorii fii ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, wata a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ìe ma an e …ìeynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ìe …ìen"
  29,34,"Ko men jippinoo…ìe lepte e yim…ìe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ìe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon"
  29,35,"Gom…óii Men accii e nden (saare), maande …ìanngunde, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe …ìen"
  29,36,"(Men nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla, jortoron √ëalannde sakkitiinde nden, wata woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ìe"
  29,37,"Kono …ìe fenni mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ìe, …ìe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìe jiccii…ìe-maayi"
  29,38,"(Men halki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. Gom…óii caambbeje ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ìe, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, ndu sakkii …ìe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ìe rentunoo…ìe"
  29,39,"(Men halki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. Gom…óii le, Muusaa addanii …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji, kono …ìe townitii ka leydi, …ìe wonaano laawotoo…ìe"
  29,40,"Kala ma…ì…ìe, Men leptirno junuubi mun …óin: no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men wuurti henndu e mun; no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe haacaango halki; no e ma…ì…ìe, mo Men mutini …óum ka leydi, no e ma…ì…ìe kadi, …ìe Men yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali too√±oowo …ìe; si ko woni, ko kam…ìe too√±unoo ko'e ma…ì…ìe"
  29,41,"Misal …ìen jogitii…ìe gaanin Alla rewetee…ói, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko …ìuri lo'ude non e cuu…ói …óin, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno …ìe annduno"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala huunde nde …ìe noddata gaanin Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,43,"∆äee ko mise …óe Men piyanta yim…ìe …ìen; ko woni tun, faamataa …óen, si wanaa anndu…ìe …ìen"
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii …óum, maande, wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  29,45,"Janngu kon ko waayinaa e maa…óa ka Deftere, √±ii…ìaa e julde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no ha…óa pankare e ko a√±inii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol …ìuri (huunde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko golloton kon"
  29,46,"Wata on wennjir yim…ìe Defte …ìen si wanaa e no …ìuri e mo∆¥∆¥irde, si wanaa hara ko …ìen too√±u…ìe e ma…ì…ìe. Wi'on: \"Men gom…óinii nden jippinaande e amen e …óen jippinaa…óe e mon. Rewetee…óo amen On e rewetee…óo mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Men jebbilanii …ìe Mo"
  29,47,"Ko wano non Men jippiniri e maa…óa Deftere nden. ∆Åen …ìe Men okki Deftere nden, hi…ìe gom…óini nde. Hino e ma…ì…ìe on gom…óin…óo nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa heefer…ìe …ìen"
  29,48,"A wonaano hi…óa janngaynoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano √±aamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnoo…ìe …ìen sikkittono"
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe e …ìer…óe …ìen okkaa…ìe ganndal. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  29,50,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Hanno jippinee e makko maandeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jertinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  29,51,"Kere yonaali …ìe wonnde Men jippinii e maa…óa Deftere nden hinde janngee e ma…ì…ìe? Wonii e …óum, yurmeende e waaju wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe"
  29,52,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii hakkunde am e moo…óon seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. ∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe meere nden …ìe yeddi Alla, ko …ìen woni sooyu…ìe …ìen"
  29,53,"Hi…ìe hawjirane lepte …óen. Si wanaano fii lajal innaangal, lepte …óen ardirayno e ma…ì…ìe juhal, hara kam…ìe …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  29,54,"Hi…ìe hawjirane lepte …óen, hara non pellet, Jahannama ko fiiltiinge heefere…ìe …ìen"
  29,55,"√ëalnde lepte …óen suddiroyta …ìe senngo dow ma…ì…ìe e ka ley koy…óe ma…ì…ìe, O daala[na …ìe]: \"Mee…óee ko gollayno…óon kon"
  29,56,Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe! Anndee leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Ko Min woni ko rewoton
  29,57,Kala wonkii mee…óay maayde. Refti ko ka Amen ruttete…óon
  29,58,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men ho…ónu …ìe ka Aljanna e cuu…ói …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley majji, ko…ìe duumotoo…ìe ton. Iskin(heskey)¬∞ mo∆¥∆¥ere njo…ìdi gollunoo…ìe, @Corrected"
  29,59,"…ìen mu√±√±ii…ìe, …ìe tuugii e Joomi ma…ì…ìe"
  29,60,"∆äuu…óii e ruugay…ói …ói yoo…ìotaako arsike majji! Ko Alla arsikata …ói wonndude e onon. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo"
  29,61,"Pellet, si a lanndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuu- li …óin e leydi ndin, O elti naange ngen e lewru ndu?\" Ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Ko honno …ìe ferlitoraa (e gom…óingol ngol)"
  29,62,"Alla no yaajinana arsike on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Himo …ìittana mo. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  29,63,"Pellet, si a lanndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu …óam O wuurnitiri leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorude?\", ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Maaku: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla!\". Si ko woni, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe haqqiltaa"
  29,64,"∆äam nguurndam aduna wonaali, si wanaa mbelee…óe e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko ho…óo laakara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno …ìe annduno"
  29,65,"Si …ìe wa…ó…óike ka laana, …ìe nodda Alla …ìe la…ì…ìinano Mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde O da…óndi …ìe ka njorndi, ontuma …ìe sirka"
  29,66,"No …ìe yeddira ko Men okki …ìe kon, awa yo …ìe dakmito! Aray ka…ìe annda"
  29,67,"E …ìee yi'aali wonnde Men wa…óii hormorde hoolniinde, yim…ìe …ìen no cifee(bifte) bannge ma…ì…ìe? E ko meere nden …ìe gom…óinta …ìe yedda neemaaji Alla …óin"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo …ìuri too√±irde wa on fefindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  29,69,"∆Åen tii…ónor…ìe e (weltingol) Men, ma Men fewnir…ìe e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  30,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  30,2,Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen foolaama
  30,3,"ka …ìuri …ìadaade e leydi ndin, kam…ìe kadi …ìaawo …ìe fooleede, …ìe fooloya"
  30,4,"e nder duu…ìi see…óaaji. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku (poolal ngal) ado e …ìaawo (maggal). Nden √±alnde, gom…óim…ìe …ìen weltota"
  30,5,"ballal Alla ngal. Himo walla mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko woni Fooloowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  30,6,"[∆äum] ko fodoore Alla. Alla lunndotaako fodoore Makko nden. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe anndaa"
  30,7,"Hi…ìe anndi ko fee√±i e nguurndam aduna, kono kam…ìe e fii laakara on, ko …ìe welsindii…ìe"
  30,8,"E …ìee miijitaaki fii ko'e-ma…ì…ìe? Alla tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, si wanaa goonga e lajal innaangal. Anndee ko …óuu…ói e yim…ìe …ìen, ko yeddu…ìe hawroygol e Joomi ma…ì…ìe"
  30,9,"E …ìee yillaaki ka leydi …ìe taskoo ko honno battane …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe wa'unoo? ∆Åen wonuno …ìur…ìe …ìe doole …ìe remi e leydi ndin …ìe wuuri e mayri …ìuri ko …ìee wuuri e mayri kon. Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addani …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji. Alla wonaali too√±oowo …ìe, kono non ko ko'e ma…ì…ìe …ìe wonno e too√±ude"
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane bonnu…ìe …ìen, ko bonande fii …ìe fennii Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ìe laatii e jalkitugol …óe"
  30,11,Ko Alla fu…ó…ói tagu ngun; refti O rutta ngu; refti ko ka Makko ruttete…óon
  30,12,"√ëalnde Darngal ngal darii, bom…ìe …ìen ta∆¥oto"
  30,13,"Woodanoytaa…ìe e kafidii…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin tefooji, …ìe woniino yeddu…ìe kafidu…ìe …ìen"
  30,14,"√ëalnde Darngal ngal darii,nden √±alnde …ìe seertoyay"
  30,15,"Si ko …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, …ìen …óon wonoyay e beeli (Aljanna) hi…ìe sa…ónee(weltine)"
  30,16,"Si tawii non ko …ìen yeddu…ìe …ìe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen e hawrugol ngol e laakara, …ìen …óon ko tawnoytee…ìe e lepte …óen"
  30,17,"Subbunhinanee Alla, tuma hiiroton e tuma weetoton"
  30,18,"Ko Kanko yettoore woodani ka kammuuli e ka leydi, e kiikii…óe e saaga √±alloton"
  30,19,"Himo yaltina ko wuuri e ndr ko maayi, O yaltina kadi ko maayi e nder ko wuuri. Himo wuurnita leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non yatainirte- …óon (e genaale mon)"
  30,20,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: wonnde O tagii on immorde e mbum-mbuldi, refti jaka ko on …ìanndike saakotoo…ìe [e leydi ndin]"
  30,21,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin : wonnde O tagiranii on e wonkiiji mon …óin, resondir…ìe, fii yo on dee∆¥u e ma…ì…ìe, O wa…ói hakkunde mon giggol e yumeende. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde yim…ìe miijitotoo…ìe"
  30,22,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e luutondirgol …óem…óe mon e mbaadiiji mon. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji andu…ìe …ìen"
  30,23,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: …óoyngol mon ngol jemma e √±alorma, e …óa…ì…ìugol mon …ìural Makko. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde yim…ìe nanoo…ìe"
  30,24,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: Himo hollira on ma∆¥e …óen kulol e tama'u (to…ìo), Himo jippinira ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitira …óam leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe"
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: nde kammu ngun e leydi ndin daroto e yamiroore Makko. Refti si O noddii on noddaandu ka leydi, e jaka onon hi…óon yalta (e genaale mon)"
  30,26,"Hino woodani (laamagol, e tagugol e toppitagol) …ìen won…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi: kala ma…ì…ìe ko …óoftii…ìe Mo"
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fu…ó…óu…óo tagu ngun, refti O ruttita ngu; ko …óum …ìuri newanaande Mo. Hino woodani sifa …ìur…óo toowude ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko woni on Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo on"
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal immorde e ko'e-mon: hara no woodani on e …ìen …ìe jeyru…óon √±aame mon, immorde e kafidal e kon ko Men arsiki on, hara hi…óon fota e …óum, hi…óon hulira …ìe wano hulirton ko'e-mon? Ko woni nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje …óen, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe"
  30,29,"Si ko woni, too√±u…ìe …ìen jokkirii belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko hommbo fewnata mo Alla majjini? Alanaa …ìe walloo…ìe"
  30,30,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina kan √±ii…ìugol [e mun]. [∆äum] ko tagu Alla ngu O tagiri yim…ìe …ìen e mun - wa…ótitugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun -. Ko …óum woni diina focciika kan; kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa"
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotoo…ìe e Makko; hulon Mo, √±innon julde nden, wata on jeye e sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  30,32,"(wano) …ìeya senndunoo…ìe diina mun kan, …ìe woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mun kon"
  30,33,"Si sa…óteende memii yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe noddira Joomi ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe ruttitii…ìe e Makko; refti si O mee…óinii …ìe yumeende immorde e Makko, e jaka fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe no kafida e Joomi mun"
  30,34,"Yo…ìe yeddu ko Men okki …ìe kon. \"Awa dakmitee, arma anndon"
  30,35,"Kaa Men jippin e ma…ì…ìe hujja (Deftere), hara honde yewta fii ko …ìe sirkaynoo kon"
  30,36,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ìe …ìen neema, …ìe weltoroo mo. Si bone memirii …ìe sabu ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ardiniri kon, e jaka hi…ìe ta∆¥oo"
  30,37,"E …ìe yi'aali wonnde Alla no ya√±√±ana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ìillina? Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe"
  30,38,"Jonnu jom-…ìadiido o hakke makko on, e …ìillii…ìe e …ìii-laawol. ∆äum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude wonande …ìeen faalaa…ìe yarluyee Alla on; ko …ìen woni maloytee…ìe …ìen. @Corrected"
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnu…óon e riba, fii on …ìeydor e jawle yim…ìe …ìen, …óum …ìeydotaako ka Alla, kala non ko okku…óon e Jakka, mo faandori…óon welayee Alla, …ìen …óon, ko sowanoytee…ìe [njo…ìdi] …ìen. @Corrected"
  30,40,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo on, refti O arsiki on, refti O wara on, refti O wuurnita on. Hara no e kafidaa…ói mon …óin wa…óay…ói go…ó…óum e …óum? Senayeewoo-dani Mo! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkata"
  30,41,"Bone on fee√±iri ka njoorndi e ka maaje, sabu ko juu…óe yim…ìe …ìen faggitii kon; fii yo O mee…óin …ìe yoga e ko …ìe huuwi; belajo'o, …ìe ruttoto"
  30,42,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane adinoo…ìe …ìen wa'unoo. Tawno ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe ko sirkoo…ìe"
  30,43,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina focciika kan, ado √±alaande arde immorde ka Alla nde ruttetaake. Nde √±alnde, …ìe seeday"
  30,44,"Kala yeddu…óo, haray geddi makko …óin no fawii mo. Kala non gollu…óo mo∆¥∆¥ere, haray ko ko'e-ma…ì…ìe …ìe hebilani (Aljanna)"
  30,45,"fii yo O yo…ìu …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, e …ìural Makko ngal. Kanko On, O yi…óaa heefer…ìe …ìen"
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: Wurtugol Mo keneeli …óin wewlinooji, e fii yo O mee…óin on e yurmeende Makko nden, e no laa…óe …óen dogira e yamiroore Makko, e fii yo o …óa…ì…ìu e …ìural Makko. Belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  30,47,"Gom…óii Men nulii ado maa…óa Nulaa…ìe haa e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, …ìe addani …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji. Men yottii e …ìen bonnu…ìe; tawi no jojji e Amen faabagol gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo kenee…ói …óin, …ói sogga duule …óen; O saakitira …óum ka weeyo no O yi…óiri; O wa…óta …óum ta∆¥e-ta∆¥e. A yi'ay to…ìo ngon no yalta hakkude mun. Si O hewtinii ngo e on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, e jaka kam…ìe hi…ìe weltoo"
  30,49,"Gom…óii …ìe laatinoke ado (to…ìo) ngon jippineede e ma…ì…ìe, ko ta∆¥inoo…ìe"
  30,50,"Ndaarii e battane yurmeende Alla nden, no O wuurnitorta leydi …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Pellet, wa…óoowo …óum On, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ìe …ìen, Kanko Ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  30,51,"[Hay] si Men nulii henndu, …ìe yi'i [gese ma…ì…ìe] …óen no soy…ói, …ìe jokkay …ìaawo …óum, hi…ìe yedda"
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maay…ìe …ìen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ìe …ìen kadi noddaandu ndun, si …ìe runtiima …ìe huccinii …ìabbe (ma…ì…ìe)"
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoowo wum…ìe …ìen e majjere ma…ì…ìe. A nanintaa si wanaa …ìen gom…óim…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen, hara ko …ìe jebbilii…ìe"
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo on e lo'ere, refti O wa…ói …ìaawo lo'ere nden cemmbe, refti O wa…ói …ìaawo cemmbe …óen lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Himo taga ko O muuyi, Ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo, Hattan…óo"
  30,55,"√ëalnde Darngal nal darotoo, bom…ìe …ìen woonday …ìe √±ii…ìaali si wanaa saanga. Ko wano nii …ìe wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)"
  30,56,"Okkaa…ìe ganndal e gom…óinal …ìen wi'a: \"Gom…óii on √±ii…ìii e ko Alla winndi kon, haa √±alnde ummital. Ko ndee woni √±alaande ummital, kono onon on anndaano"
  30,57,"Nden √±alnde, ngantooji …óin nafoytaa too√±u…ìe …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni ko …óa…ì…ìiretee welayee [Alla]. @Corrected"
  30,58,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii …ìe Aaya, …ìen yeddu…ìe wi'ay: \"On wonaali, si wanaa meerentee…ìe"
  30,59,Ko wano nii Alla notira e …ìer…óe …ìen …ìe anndaa
  30,60,"Mu√±√±o, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goona. Wata …ìe hoynuma …ìen hoyfine"
  31,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  31,2,"∆äee, ko Aayeeje Deftere √±e√±aande nden"
  31,3,Ko nde peewal e yurmeende wonannde mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen
  31,4,"…ìen √±innoo…ìe julde nden, …ìe totta aakkal on, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe yananaa…ìe (fii laakara)"
  31,5,"Ko …ìen woni e peewal immorde e Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìe, ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  31,6,"Hino woodi e yim…ìe …ìen, soodiroowo mbelee…óe konngu…ói haa o majjira e laawol Alla ngol ko aldaa e ganndal, o jogitora (Aayeeje) …óen jalnitgol. ∆Åen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte hoynooje"
  31,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e makko, o huccitira(runtora) townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali …óe, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. weltanir-mo lepte muusu…óe"
  31,8,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, hino woodani …ìe Aljannaaji neema"
  31,9,"Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe ton, …óum ko fodoore Alla goongunde. Ko Kanko woni On Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  31,10,"O tagirii kammuuli …óin ko aldaa e tugaale, …óe yi'oton; O werlii ka leydi pelle fii wata ndi dillidu e mon; O saaki e mayri kala ruugayngel. Men jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, Men fu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji teddu…ói"
  31,11,"∆äum …óoo ko tagu Alla. Hollee Lam ko …ói (rewoton …óin) gaanin Makko tagi?\" Si ko woni, too√±u…ìe …ìen no e majjere …ìanngunde"
  31,12,"Gom…óii Men okkii Luqmaan √±en∆¥al: \"Wonnde yettu Alla. Kala yettu…óo, haray ko hoore-makko o yettani; kala non yeddu…óo, anndu pellet, Alla ko Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  31,13,"Janto tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo ge…óal makko on, hari himo waajoo mo: \"Ko an …ìinngel am, wata a sirkan Alla. Pellet, sirku on ko too√±e maw…óe"
  31,14,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on […óoftagol] jibim…ìe mo …ìen; yumma makko saawirii mo lo'ere e hoore lo'ere: entugol mo ngol, ko e nder duu…ìi …ói…ói. \"Wonnde yettam e jinnaa…ìe maa …ìen. Ko ka Am woni wa…ótinirde nden"
  31,15,"Si …ìe tii…ónorii ma fii sirkangol Lam e ko a alanaa …óum ganndal, wata a …óofto …ìe; wonndir e ma…ì…ìe ka aduna …óoo mo∆¥∆¥ere. Jokku laawol on ruttii…óo e Am. Refti ko ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi yeetitoo on, ko gollayno…óon"
  31,16,"Ko an …ìinngel am, anndu …óen [golle bon…óe maa mo∆¥∆¥e], si fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi fo√±√±e, …óum wona e fetere, maa ka kammuuli maa ka leydi, Alla artiray nde. Pellet, Alla ko Newii…óo, Humpitii…óo"
  31,17,"Ko an yo …ìinngel am, √±ii…ìnu julde nden, yamiraa mo∆¥∆¥ere, ha…óaa ≈ãi√±ere(pankare), mu√±√±o-…óaa e ko he…ìu-maa. Pellet, …óum ko jeyaa…óum e fiyakkuji maw…ói. @Corrected"
  31,18,"Wata fal yim…ìe …ìen yeeso maa ngon, wata a yahru ka leydi √±aa∆¥agol. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa kala √±aa∆¥otoo…óo mantoo"
  31,19,"Hakindo e yahdu-maa ndun, joltinaa(ustu) hito maa ngon; ko …ìuri a√±eede e hitooji …óin, pellet, ko luukaadu mbabba"
  31,20,"E on yi'aali wonnde Alla eltanii on ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi? O huu…ìitiri on neemaaji Makko fee√±u…ói e suu…óii…ói. Hino woodi e yim…ìe …ìen, on wennjiroowo e fii Alla, ko aldaa e gannndal, wanaa peewal, wanaa Deftere jabunde"
  31,21,"Si …ìe wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", …ìe wi'a: \"Si ko woni, men jokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen\"; e hay si tawii seytaane wonii hino nodda …ìe e lepte dulboowe ngen"
  31,22,"Kala jebbilu…óo yeeso mun ngon faade e Alla, hara ko o mo∆¥∆¥in…óo, gom…óii o jaggiima e …ìoggol tii…óungol. Ko ka Alla woni battane fiyakuuji …óin"
  31,23,"Kala yeddu…óo, wata keeferaaku makko sunine. Ko ka Amen woni ruttorde ma…ì…ìe, Men humpita …ìe ko …ìe huuwunoo. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo jaati …ìer…óe"
  31,24,"Men dakmitay …ìe see…óa, refti Men forsa…ìe e lepte tekku…óe"
  31,25,"Pellet, si a lamndike …ìe : \"Ko hommbo tagi kammiili …óin e leydi ndin?\" Ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Alla!\" Maaku: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla!\". Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe anndaa"
  31,26,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla, ko Kanko woni Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  31,27,"Hay si tawii ko woni ka hoore leydi kon e le…ó…óe, [settiraama] karambi, maayo ngon …ìeydora (wontugol ndaha) …ìaawo …óum, yeru maaje jee…ói…ói, konngu…ói Alla …óin lannataa. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  31,28,"Tagugol on e immintingol wonaali, si wanaa wa (tagugol) wonkii gooti. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  31,29,"E a yi'aali wonnde Alla no naada jemma on e nder √±alora on, O naada √±alorma kadi e nder jemma on, O eltii kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal? E wonnde Alla ko Humpitii…óo ko golloton kon"
  31,30,"∆äum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo], ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga, e wonnde kon ko …ìe noddata gaanin Makko, ko …óum woni meere nden, e wonnde ko Alla woni Toowu…óo, Mawnu…óo On"
  31,31,"E a yi'aali wonnde laa…óe …óen hino dogira ka maayo e neema Alla, fii yo O hollu on maandeeji Makko …óin? Wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde kala heewu…óo-mu√±al, yettoowo (neema)"
  31,32,"Si tawii morloo…óe(bempejje) hippirii…ìe wa duule [maa pelle], …ìe nodday Alla, hara hi…ìe la…ì…ìinani Mo dewal; tuma nde O da…óndunoo…ìe ka njorndi, tawi no e ma…ì…ìe hakindii…óo. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa kala heewu…óo janfa, keefeero"
  31,33,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! Hulee Joomi mon, hulon √±alaande, nde baaba duncanoytaa …ìi…ó…óo mun, wanaa …ìi…ó…óo on kadi duncanoyta ben mun hay huunde. Pellet, fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata hodu on e Alla, (seytaane) hodoowo"
  31,34,"Pellet, ko ka Alla woni anndal Darngal, Himo jippina to…ìo; Himo anndi ko woni ka nder renngaaji. Wonkii (woo) anndaa ko ki faggitoto janngo, wonkii (woo) kadi anndaa ko e leydi honndi maayata. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo, Humpitii…óo"
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  32,2,"Jippineede Deftere nden, sikke woo alaa e mu'un, ko immorde ka Jey…óo winndere nden"
  32,3,"Walla …ìe wi'ay kanko (Muhammadu) o fefindi nde? Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo a jertin yim…ìe, …ìe jertinoowo araano e mun ado maa…óa, belajo'o, …ìe feeway"
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, e nder bal…óe jeegoo. Refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arski\". Alanaa on gaanin Makko, gi…óo wanaa tefoowo. E on waajitotaako? @Corrected"
  32,5,"Himo fewja fiyaakuuji …óin ka kammu haa ka leydi, refti …ói ∆¥eenga ka Makko, e √±alaande nde emmbere mun woni, duu…ìi ujunere e ko limoton"
  32,6,"On [fewjoowo fii …óum on], ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói e fee√±u…ói, Foolu…óo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  32,7,On labin…óo kala huunde nde O tagi. O fu…ó…ói tagude ne…ó…óanke ndin e loopal
  32,8,"refti O wa…ói geyngol makko ngol, e sortondiral, immorde ndihal [maniiyu] lo'u…óam"
  32,9,"refi O fotndindiri mo, O wutti e makko Ruuhu Makko on. O wa…óani on nan…óe, e gii…óe e …ìer…óe. [Kono] fan…óii ko yettonton"
  32,10,"∆Åe wi': \"E nee, si min majjii ka leydi, eyoo men wontay e tagu hesu?\" Ko woni kam…ìe e hawrugol e Joomi ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìe yeddu…ìe […óum]"
  32,11,"Maaku: \"Ko hunnata on, ko malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaa…óo on. Refti ko ka Joomi mon ruttete…óon"
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'ayno, tuma nde bom…ìe …ìen ugginta ko'e-ma…ì…ìe ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe! [l∆Åe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, men yi'ii men nanii, rutton men, men golla ko mo∆¥∆¥i; menen men yananaama"
  32,13,"Sinno Men muuyuno, Men okkayno kala wonkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : \"Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yim…ìe, …ìe denndaangal"
  32,14,"Mee…óiree (lepte …óen) sabu welsindagol mon hawrugol e ndee √±alaande mon …óoo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. Mee…óiree lepte luttal, sabu ko huuwayno…óon kon"
  32,15,"Anndee ko gom…óinta Aayeeje Amen …óen, ko …ìen taw…ìe si …ìe waajoraama …óe, …ìe suuyiray sujjugol, …ìe subbuhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe, kam…ìe …ìe townitotaako"
  32,16,"Becce ma…ì…ìe …óen hino wo…ó…óitoo e lelor…óe …óen, hi…ìe noddira Joomi ma…ì…ìe kulol e tama'u; e kon ko Men arsiki …ìe, hi…ìe wintoo"
  32,17,"Wonkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa …ìe e ko …ìu…ì…ìinta …ìernde, …óum ko njo…ìdi ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  32,18,"E on laatii…óo gom…óin…óo wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), …ìe fotataa"
  32,19,"Si ko …ìen om…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hino woodani …ìe Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu ko…ìe gollaynoo kon"
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko …ìe faasiqii…ìe, haray femporde …ìen …óon nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala …ìe faalaa yaltugol e magge, …ìe ruttitee e magge, …ìe wi'anee: \"Mee…óee lepte Yiite nge fennayo…óon ngen"
  32,21,"Ma Men mee…óinir …ìe lepte aduna, ado lepte maw…óe …óen (laakara), belajo'o, …ìe ruttitoto"
  32,22,"Alaa …ìur…óo too√±ude wano waajoraa…óo Aayeeje Joomi mun …óen, refti o …óuurnii …óe ! Pellet, Menen, ko Men yoftotoo…ìe e bom…ìe …ìen"
  32,23,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, - wata a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Men wa…ói nde …óoworde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  32,24,"Men wa…ói e ma…ì…ìe ardii…ìe, …óowiroo…ìe (yim…ìe …ìen) yamiroore Amen, nde …ìe mu√±√±inoo, …ìe woni yananaa…ìe e Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko senndoyta hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, √ëalnde Darngal, e kon ko …ìe lurraynoo e fii mun"
  32,26,"E fee√±anaali …ìe, no foti …óuu…óude e ko Men halki ado ma…ì…ìe e gire, hi…ìe yaha e ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe? Pellet, no e …óum, tasakuyeeji ! E …ìee haqqiltaa"
  32,27,"E …ìe yi'aali, wonnde Me…óen soggira ndiyam …óam ka leydi hokkundi, Men yaltinira …óam remuru, ndu neemoraa…ói ma…ì…ìe e kam…ìe √±aamata e mun? E …ìe yi'ataa"
  32,28,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  32,29,"Maaku: \"√ëalnde uddial ngal, ko heefer…ìe …ìen gom…óinoyta nafoytaa…ìe, wanaa kam…ìe woni nennantee…ìe"
  32,30,"∆äuurno …ìe, ha…ì…ìito-…óaa. Kam…ìe kan, ko …ìe ha…ì…ìitii…ìe (lepte)"
  33,1,"Ko an yo Annabiijo! Hulu Alla, wata a …óofto heefer…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe …ìen. Pellet, Alla laatike Anndu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  33,2,"Jokku ko wahayinaa kon e maa…óa, immorde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, Alla laatike Humpitii…óo ko golloton kon"
  33,3,Fawo e Alla. Alla yonii fawetee…óo e mun
  33,4,"Alla wa…óanaali ne…ó…óanke …ìer…óe …ói…ói e nder fulkuru makko. O wa…óaali kadi resondiraa…ìe mon …ìen …ìe nanndinirton, neeniraa…ìe mon. O wa…óaali kadi nodditiray…ìe on (baaba …ìen), …ìi…ó…ìe moo…óon. ∆äum moo…óon, ko kongol mon [yaltungol e] kunndule mon. Alla non, no daala goonga, ko Kanko woni fewnoowo e focciingol ngol"
  33,5,"Noddiree …ìe baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen: ko …óum …ìuri nun…óude ka Alla. Si tawii non on anndaa baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, haray ko musi…ó…ìe mon ka diina e heftodii…ìe mon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on e ko woopoton (faayon) e mun, kono (on bakkondinay e) ko faandori…óon …ìer…óe mon …óen. Alla laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  33,6,"Ko Annabiijo on …ìuri hanndude e gom…óim…ìe …ìen diini ko'e ma…ì…ìe; suddii…ìe makko …ìen, ko neeniraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe. Joomiraa…ìe en…óamaaji …ìen, ko yoga ma…ì…ìe …ìuri hanndude yoga [e ndonndi ndin] ka Deftere Alla, diini gom…óim…ìe …ìen e feru…ìe …ìen, si wanaa hara on wa…óan weldii…ìe mon […ìe ronataa] …ìen mo∆¥∆¥ere. ∆äum wonii ko winndaa ka deftere"
  33,7,"Janto tuma nde Men ∆¥ettidunoo e Annabaa…ìe …ìen ahadi ma…ì…ìe, e ma'a an kadi, e Nuuhu, e Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa …ìi…ó…óo Maryama on: Men ∆¥ettidi e ma…ì…ìe ahadi tii…óundi"
  33,8,"fii no [Alla] lamdora goongu…ìe …ìen e goonga ma…ì…ìe kan. O hebilanii yeddu…ìe …ìen, lepte muusuu…óe"
  33,9,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe ! Annditee neema Alla on e dow moo…óon, tuma nde koneeli arunoo on, Men wurti e ma…ì…ìe henndu e konuuli, ngu on yi'aali. Alla siforii Rentu…óo ko golloton"
  33,10,"Tuma nde …ìe ardirannoo on, ka senngo dow mon e ka ley [saare] mon, e tuma nde gite oo√±inoo, …ìer…óe …óen hewtiri ka looko∆¥e, hi…óon jikka Alla (ontuma) jikke luutondir…óe"
  33,11,"Ko …óon gom…óim…ìe …ìen njariba, …ìe dilliniraa dillere sa…ótunde"
  33,12,"Janto kadi, tuma nde naafiqii…ìe …ìen, e …ìen …ìe √±awu woni e …ìer…óe mun wi'aynoo: \"Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fodaali men, si wanaa hodo"
  33,13,"E tuma nde fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe wi'unoo: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe Yathrib ! √ëii…ìirde alanaa on (…óoo), yiltitee [ka mon]\". Fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe no waynitoo Annabiijo on, hi…ìe wi'a : \"Cuu…ói amen …óin ko na huncii\", hara non wanaa …ói huncii…ói: …ìe faandaaki, si wanaa dogugol"
  33,14,"Hay si tawno (ay…ìe) …ìen naatiranno …ìe …ìannge mayre, refti …ìe lanndaa fitina (yeddugol), pellet, …ìe wonayno e mun, …ìe leelnataano e …óum, si wanaa see…óa"
  33,15,"hara le gom…óii …ìe ahodiino e Alla ko adii, wonnde …ìe runtotaako …ìabbe. Ahadi Alla ndin non, ndi laatike lannditorteendi"
  33,16,"Maaku: \"Dogugol nafataa on, si on dogu maayde maa hare; haray …óum, on dakmitetaake, si wanaa see…óa"
  33,17,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo woni da…óndoowo on e Alla, si O faandanike on bone, maa si O faandanike on yurmeende?\" ∆Åe he…ìantaa ko'e ma…ì…ìe gaanin Alla, gi…óo wanaa ballo"
  33,18,"Gom…óii Alla no anndi falaotoo…ìe …ìen e mon, e …ìen wi'anoo…ìe musi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen :\"Aree e amen\", hara non …ìe arataa e hare nden, si wanaa see…óa"
  33,19,"ko wuddan …ìe on. Si kulol ngol arii, a yi'ay hi…ìe ndaare, hara gite ma…ì…ìe no yiilora wa mo maayde suddaa e mun. Si kulo ngol non yehii, …ìe laggora …óem…óe muusu…óe, wuddangol mo∆¥∆¥ere nden. ∆Åen …óon, …ìe gom…óinaali, Alla bonnii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen. ∆äum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  33,20,"Hi…ìe sikka koneeli …óin yahataa. Hay si koneeli …óin artii, …ìee [naafiqii…ìe] yelotono sinno hara nun hi…ìe ka ladde hakkunde yim…ìe ladde …ìen, hara hi…ìe lanndo fii mon. Hay si …ìe tawtodano e mon, …ìe ha…ìataano si wanaa see…óa nii"
  33,21,"Gom…óii laatanike on e Nulaa…óo Alla on, √±emtinal mo∆¥∆¥al, wonannde on jortii…óo Alla, e √ëalaande sakkitiinde nden, o jantii Alla ko …óuu…ói"
  33,22,"Nde gom…óim…ìe …ìen yi'unoo koneeli …óin, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko …óum woni ko Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fodi men; haray Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on goongii\". ∆äum …ìeydaali …ìe, si wanaa gom…óinal e jebbilaare"
  33,23,"Hino e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, wor…ìe hunnu…ìe ko …ìe ahodi e Alla kon : hino e ma…ì…ìe timmin…óo takke mun …óen (haa o sahodinaa), hino e ma…ì…ìe kadi ha…ì…ìitii…óo; …ìe wa…ótitaali (ahadi ndin) mbattiigu"
  33,24,"Fii yo Alla yo…ìir hunnu…ìe …ìen sabu goongude ma…ì…ìe, O lepta naafiqii…ìe …ìen, si Mo yi…ói, maa O ja…ìana …ìe tuubuubuyee. Tawde pellet, Alla laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  33,25,"Alla ruttidii yeddu…ìe …ìen e tikkere ma…ì…ìe nden, …ìe he…ìaali mo∆¥∆¥ere. Alla yonii gom…óim…ìe …ìen e hare. Alla siforii Cemmbe e Poolal"
  33,26,"O jipiini …ìen wallindirnoo…ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe Defte …ìen, ka tataaji ma…ì…ìe …óin, O weddii …óen∆¥ere e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe; fedde goo (e ma…ì…ìe) hi…óon wara, hi…óon daha kadi fede goo"
  33,27,"O ronini on leydi ma…ì…ìe, e galleeji ma…ì…ìe, e jawle ma…ì…ìe, e leydi ndi on tippaano e mun. Alla siforii hattan…óo kala huunde"
  33,28,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Maakan suddii…ìe maa …ìen: \"Si wonii ko nguurndam aduna faala…óon e cu…óaari majjam, haray aree mi dakmita on, mi seera on [ontuma] cergal mo∆¥∆¥al"
  33,29,"Si tawii non ko Alla faala…óon, e Nulaa…óo Makko on, e galle laakara …óen, haray pellet, Alla maranii mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe …ìen e moo…óon, njo…ìdi mawndi"
  33,30,"Ko onon yo suddii…ìe Annabiijo on ! Kala addu…óo e moo…óon bone …ìanngu…óo, lepte …óen sowirante mo cowalle …ói…ói! ∆äum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  33,31,"Kala e moo…óon …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i, Men yo…ìiray mo njo…ìdi makko ndin laa…ìi …ói…ói, Me…óen marani mo kadi, arsike teddu…óo"
  33,32,"Ko onon yo suddii…ìe Annabiijo! On wa'aa wano gooto e suddii…ìe …ìen. Si on gom…óii, haray wata on yergin konngol, sakko on mo √±awu [tuuyo] woni e …ìernde mun tam∆¥inoo. Wowlon konngol mo∆¥∆¥ol"
  33,33,"√ëii…ìee ka cuu…ói mon; wata on fe√±√±inir cu…óaari mon, wano wirtaare majjere adinoo…ìe. √ëii…ìnee Julde nden, totton askal on, …óofto…óon Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on. Anndee ko Alla faandii, ko ittanta on e tuu…óe, onon yim…ìe suudu [Annabiijo], O la…ì…ìinira on la…ì…ìingol"
  33,34,"Jantee ko wonaa e janngeede ka cuu…ói mon, immorde e Aayeeje Alla, e Sunna. Pellet, Alla laatike Newii…óo, Humpitii…óo"
  33,35,"Pellet, juul…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e juul…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e …óoftii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e …óoftii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e goongu…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e goongu…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e mu√±√±ii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e mu√±√±ii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e yankinii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e yankinii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e sakkotoo…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e sakkotoo…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e hooroo…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e hooroo…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e wor…ìe reenoo…ìe farjuuji mun e rew…ìe reenoo…ìe farjuuji mun, e wor…ìe jantotoo…ìe Alla ko …óuu…ói …ìen e rew…ìe jantotoo…ìe …ìen: Alla maranii …ìen, haforanal e njo…ìdi mawndi"
  33,36,"Alanaa gom…ói…óo gorko, wanaa gom…óin…óo debbo, si Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on √±aawii fiyaaku, nde su…ìagol e fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe on. Kala non yeddu…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray o majjii majjere …ìanngunde"
  33,37,"Janto tuma maakanayno-…óaa on mo Alla neemini e mun, mo∆¥∆¥u-…óaa e makko: \"Jogitano suddii…óo maa on, hoore-maa, hulaa Alla\", hi…óa suu…óa e fonndo maa, ko Alla fe√±√±inta. Hi…óa hula yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko Alla fotu-…óaa hulude. Tuma Zaydu huntunoo e (suddii…óo) on haaju, Men resin-maa mo, fii wata …ìittere wonu e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, e (resugol) suddii…ìe nodditiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, si …ìen huntii e ma…ì…ìe haaju. Yamiroore Alla nden laatike golleteende"
  33,38,"Feloore alanaa Annabiijo on, e kon ko Alla daginai mo, …óum ko √±aawoore Alla e …ìen fe∆¥∆¥u…ìe ado makko. √ëaawoore Alla nde wonii e…ì…ìaande hoddiraande"
  33,39,"∆Åen yottiinoo…ìe nule Alla …óen, …ìe no hula Mo, …ìe hula go…ó…óo goo si wanaa Alla. Alla yonii hasboowo"
  33,40,"Muhammadu wonaali baaba hay goot e wor…ìe mon, ko [o] woni, ko Nulaa…óo Alla e timmoode Annabaa…ìe. Alla laatike Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  33,41,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe, jantoree Alla jantoore …óuu…óunde"
  33,42,Subhinee Mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe
  33,43,"Ko Kanko woni yurmetee…óo on, -e Malaa'ikaa…ìe Makko …ìen (du'orana on), - fii no O yaltinira on e ni…ìe faade e annoora. O siforii hinnotoo…óo gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral ma…ì…ìe ngal √±alnde …ìe hawrata e Makko, ko \"Salaam\" [kisiyee], O maranii …ìe mbarjaari teddundi"
  33,45,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men nulirii ma [fii yo wonu] seedii…óo, e wewlinoowo e jertinoowo"
  33,46,"e noddoowo faade e Alla, du≈ãayee Makko; e pitilol jal…ìungol"
  33,47,"Wewlinir gom…óim…ìe …ìen, wonnde no woodani …ìe ka Alla, …ìural mawnungal"
  33,48,"Wata a …óofto heefer…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe …ìen, …óuurno (e) lorra ma…ì…ìe kan, fawo-…óaa e Alla. Sabu Alla yonii ka fawee"
  33,49,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Si resii rew…ìe gom…óim…ìe …ìen, refti on seerii …ìe ado on meemondirde e ma…ì…ìe, haray alanaa on e ma…ì…ìe, edda mo …ìe eddinotoo. Dakmitiree …ìe [njoo…ìa], seeriron …ìe cergal la…ìaangal"
  33,50,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men daginanii ma suddii…ìe maa …ìen …ìe jonnu-…óaa te≈ãe mun …ìen, e …ìen [hor…ìe] …ìe jeyru-…óaa √±aamo maa, e …ìen [dahaa…ìe] …ìe Alla neldu-maa, e jiw…ìe bappa maa, e jiw…ìe yaayiraa…ìe maa, e jiw…ìe kaawu-maa, e jiw…ìe neeniraa…ìe maa, - …ìen feridunoo…ìe e maa, - e suddii…óo gom…óin…óo, si o ye…óii hoore-makko Annabiijo on, si Annabiijo on kadi faandike resugol mo : …óum ko ko heerani maa, gaanin gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko Men farli e ma…ì…ìe kon, e fii suddii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e ko …ìe jeytiri √±aame ma…ì…ìe …óen, fii wata …ìi…óteende wonu e maa…óa. Alla laatike haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  33,51,"Hi…óa nennintina on mo yi…óu-…óaa (nennintinnde) e ma…ì…ìe, …ìa…ótinaa e maa…óa on mo yi…óu-…óaa. E on mo …óa…ì…ìu-…óaa (belagol ka mun) e …ìen …ìe nennitu-…óaa, bakkaaku woo fawaaki ma. Ko …óum …ìuri …ìadaade e ko …ìu…ì…ìinta …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, hara …ìe sunotaako, …ìe weltora kadi ko okku-…óaa …ìe kon, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe. Alla no Anndi ko woni e …ìer…óe mon. Alla laatike Anndu…óo, Mu√±√±ii…óo"
  33,52,"Rew…ìe …ìen dagitantaako ma …ìaawo […ìee …óoo], wanaa nde wa…ótitirtaa …ìe genndiraa…ìe goo, hay si ≈ãari …ìen …óon haawnii ma; si wanaa …ìe jeyru-…óaa √±aamo maa …ìen. Alla laatike tommbii…óo kala huunde"
  33,53,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe ! Wata on naatu ka cuu…ói Annabiijo on, si wanaa hara on nodda e √±aametee, hara wanaa yo on habbito ko …ìenndi ka makko. Kono si on noddaa ma, naatee. Si on √±aamii, sentee, hara on …óa…ì…ìaali haala. Anndon …óum moo…óon, hino lorraynoo Annabiijo on, kono o hersa (haalannde) on, Alla non …óalataa [yamirde] goonga. Si on lanndoto (suddii…ìe makko) …ìen haaju, lanndoree …ìe …ìaawo wirngallo: ko …óum moo…óon, …ìuri laa…ìannde …ìer…óe mon e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe. Haananaa on nde lorroton Nulaa…óo Alla on, wanaa nde resoton suddii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen …ìaawo makko, poomaa; pellet, wa…óugol mon …óum, wonii ko mawni ka Alla"
  33,54,"Si on fe√±√±inii huunde, maa on suu…óii nde, pellet, Alla laatike anndu…óo kala huunde"
  33,55,"Bakkaatu fawaaki …ìe e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, wanaa kadi …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, wanaa banndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, wanaa e …ìi…ó…ìe banndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, wanaa e …ìi…ó…ìe mi√±√±iraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, wanaa e rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, wanaa e …ìen …ìe …ìe jeyiri √±aame ma…ì…ìe. Hulee Alla (yo suddii…ìe). Pellet, Alla siforii seedii…óo kala huunde"
  33,56,"Pellet, Alla e Malaa'ikaa…ìe Makko …ìen, hi…ìe du'anaade Annabiijo on; ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe, juulee e makko, torano…óon [Mo] kisiyee"
  33,57,"Pellet, …ìen lorroo…ìe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, Alla hu…óii …ìen aduna e laakara, O hebilanii …ìe kadi lepte hoynooje"
  33,58,"∆Åen kadi lorroo…ìe gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e hoore ko …ìe faggitaaki, gom…óii …ìe ronndike fenaande e bakkaatu …ìanngu…óo"
  33,59,"Ko an yo Annabiijo! Maakan suddii…ìe maa …ìen, e jiw…ìe maa …ìen, e genndiraa…ìe gom…óim…ìe …ìen, nde …ìe joltinta e ma…ì…ìe, wutteeji ma…ì…ìe …óin: ko …óum …ìurata …ìa…ótaade, nde …ìe annditetee, hara …ìe torraaka. Alla laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  33,60,"Pellet, si naafiqii…ìe …ìen ha…óitaaki, e …ìen …ìe √±awu (sikkitaare) woni e …ìer…óe mun, e fena-fenta'en ka saare Madiina, ma Men wurtite e ma…ì…ìe, refi …ìe kawtirtaa e maa…óa ton, si wanaa see…óa"
  33,61,"Ko hu…óaa …ìe. Kala ka …ìe tawaa, ko …ìe nanngetee …ìe, …ìe waree wargol"
  33,62,"∆äum ko sunna Alla e …ìen wulinoo…ìe ko adii. A he…ìantaa laawol (sunna) Alla ngol, battiigu"
  33,63,"Yim…ìe …ìen o lanndo maa fii Darngal. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal daragol maggal, ko ka Alla woni\". E ko anndin maa, wonnde no hasii hara Darngal ngal …ìadike"
  33,64,"Pellet, Alla hu…óii heefer…ìe …ìen, O kammbiranii …ìe kadi dulboowe"
  33,65,"ko …ìe luttoo…ìe ton poomaa. ∆Åe he…ìataa gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  33,66,"√ëalnde geece ma…ì…ìe …óen waylitetee ka Yiite, …ìe wi'ay: \"Ee jalla amen! Hara men …óoftino Alla, men …óoftii Nulaa…óo on"
  33,67,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, Menen men …óofti hooree…ìe amen e maw…ìe amen, …ìe majjini men e laawol ngol"
  33,68,"Joomi amen, tottu …ìe cowanlle …ói…ói e lepte …óen, hu…óaa …ìe kuddi mawndi"
  33,69,"Ko onon yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe! Wata on wa'u wa …ìen lorrunoo…ìe Muusaa, Alla wo…ó…óini mo e ko …ìe wi'i kon, tawde o wonii teddu…óo ka Alla"
  33,70,"Ko on yo …ìen gom…óim…ìe! Hulee Alla, wowlon konngol feewungol"
  33,71,"[Si on wa…óii …óum], O mo∆¥∆¥inanay on golle mon, O haforana on junuubi mon. Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray o maliraama maloore mawnde"
  33,72,"Men wee…ìitii hoolaare nden e dow kammuuli …óin, e leydi ndin e pelle …óen, …ói ha…óitii ronndagol nde, …ói huli (battane) majji, ne…ó…óo on kan ronndii nde; tawde pellet, o wonii …óuu…óu…óo-too√±ude [hoore-mun], majjaa…óo [battane …óum]"
  33,73,"[Ne…ó…óo on ronndiraama …óum], no Alla leptira naafiqii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e sirkoo…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e sirkoo…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, e (no) Alla ja…ìirana gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen tuububuyee. Alla laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  34,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On jey…óo kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Hino woodani Mo kadi yettoore ka laakara. Ko Kanko woni √ëee√±o, Humpitii…óo"
  34,2,"Himo anndi ko naatata ka leydi, e ko yaltata e mayri, ko jippotoo iwra ka kammu e ko ∆¥awata e maggu. Ko Kanko woni Hinnotoo, Haforoowo"
  34,3,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'i: \"Darngal ngal arataa men\". Maaku: \"aa'a! Mi woondirii Joomi am! pellet, ko aray e mon. [Joomi ma] ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói. Huunde wirnanaaki Mo, ko fotata e abbere jarra, woni ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Wanaa ko …ìuri …óum fan…óude, wanaa ko …ìuri …óum mawnude, si wanaa no e deftere fe√±√±innde"
  34,4,"Fii yo O yo…ìoy …ìen gom…óim…ìe, …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói. ∆Åen …óon, hino woodani …ìe haforaneede, e arsike teddu…óo"
  34,5,"∆Åen non yaccii …ìe e bonnitugol Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte, immorde e …ìur…óe muusude"
  34,6,"∆Åen okkaa…ìe ganndal hino yi'ira jippiniraande nden e maa…óa, immorde ka Joomi maa, ko kayre woni goonga, hinde fewnira e laawol Foolu…óo, Yettinii…óo On"
  34,7,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen kadi wi'i: \"On accay men tinndina on fii gorko, mo no humpita on, wonnde si on muncitaama kala muncitannde, on wontoyay e tagu hesu"
  34,8,"O fefindi fenaande e hoore Alla? Kaa hara ko jinna nanngi mo? Si ko woni, …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa laakara on, …ìe wonii e lepte e majjere wo…ó…óiinde (goonga)"
  34,9,"E …ìee yi'aali ko woni yeeso maa…ìe e ko woni …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Si Men muuyiino, Men munnirayno …ìe leydi ndin, maa Men fukkina e ma…ì…ìe ta∆¥ontine (lepte), immorde ka kammu. Wonii e …óum, maande, wonannde kala jeyaa…óo ruttotoo…óo (e Joomi mun)"
  34,10,"Gom…óii Men okkii Daawuuda …ìural, immorde e Amen. [Men wi'i]: \"Ko onon pelle e colli, subbunhinodee e makko. Men newinani mo (tafugol) njamndi ndin"
  34,11,"(Men wi'ani mo wonnde): \"Gollu wutteeji njamndi, e…ì…ìaa ka tafoodi. Gollon golle mo∆¥∆¥e, pellet, ko Mi Reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  34,12,"(Men eltani kadi) Sulaymaana henndu ndun: dawol mayru ko yeru (yaadu) lewru, kirndol mayru kadi ko yeru (yaadu) lewu. Men honcinani mo …ìunndu sila (kire). Hino jinnaaji …óin, golliraynoo…ói yeeso makko, e du≈ãayee Joomi Makko. Kala oo√±iingii e majji, gaay e yamiroore Amen nden, Men mee…óina ngii lepte dul…ìoowe ngen"
  34,13,"Hi…ói gollana mo ko o faalaa: gila e tataaji, e nanndollaaji, e loo…óe wa'u…óe wa beeli, e payan…óe fe≈ãii…óe. \"Gollee, onon …ìeynguure Daawuuda, yetton (Alla)\", fan…óii e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen, yettoowo (Lam)"
  34,14,"Nde Men √±aawunoo e makko maayde nden, anndinaali …ói fii maayde makko nden, si wanaa gannguuji leydi(moo∆¥u) …óin, hino √±aama tuggordu makko ndun. Nde o fukkinoo, fee√±ani jinnaaji …óin, wonnde si …ói anndunoo ko wirnii, …ói √±ii…ìataano e lepte [jeyaagu] hoynooje"
  34,15,"Gom…óii wonaniino yim…ìe Saba'i …ìen e ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe …óin, maande; gese …ói…ói ka bannge √±aamo e ka nano. (Men wi'ani …ìe): \"√ëaamee e arsike Joomi mon, yetton Mo. Leydi ndin ko laa…ìundi, e Joomiraawo Haforoowo"
  34,16,"(Kono) …ìe …óuunii. Men wurti e ma…ì…ìe ndiyam waame, Men wa…ótitani …ìe gese ma…ì…ìe …óen …ói…ói, gese (goo) …ói…ói, mar…óe √±aametee haa…óu…óo, e (le…ó…óe) du…ì…ìeeje, e huunde e jaa…ìe see…óaaje"
  34,17,"Ngool (yaggingol), Men yo…ìir…ìe ko …ìe yeddi kon. E hara Men yo…ìay si wanaa yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  34,18,"Men wa…ói hakkune ma…ì…ìe e ko…óooli …ói Men wa…ói barki e mun …óin, ko…óooli fee√±ondir…ói, Men e…ì…ìi e majji yaadu. (Men wi'ani …ìe): \"Yehee ton jemmaaji e √±alormaaji, ko on hoolii…ìe"
  34,19,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, wo…ó…óindir hakkunde yaaduuji amen\", …ìe too√±i ko'e ma…ì…ìe, Men wa…óti fillitee …ìe fii mun, Men senndindiri …ìe hattirde e senndirgol. Pellet, wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde kala heewu…óo mu√±al, yettoowo (neema)"
  34,20,"Gom…óii Ibuliisa goonginii jikke mun …óen e ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe jokki mo, si wanaa fedde e gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  34,21,"E doole alanaa mo e dow ma…ì…ìe, cemmbe (wurtugol), si wanaa tun, ko fii no Men anndira on gom…óin…óo laakara e on won…óo e sikke fii mun. Joomi maa non, e dow kala huunde, ko O reenu…óo"
  34,22,"Maaku: \"Noddee …óin …ói …óaynitor…óon [ rewetee…ói] gaanin Alla. ∆äi jeyaa hay yeru abbere jarra, ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi. Alanaa …ói e …óin (kammuuli e leydi ndin) kafidaa…óo (ge…ìal), alanaa Mo e …óin, hay wallondirtee…óo"
  34,23,"Tefoore woo nafataa ka Makko, si wanaa on Mo O du≈ãanii. Haa si …óen∆¥ere nden yaltinaama e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'a: \"Ko hon…óum Joomi mon daali?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Ko goonga kan; ko Kanko woni Toowu…óo, Maw…óo On"
  34,24,"Maaku: \"Kon hombo woni arsikiroowo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla. Ko si ko menen maa si ko onon, woni e peewal maa e nder majjere …ìanngunde"
  34,25,"Maaku: \"On lamnditoytaake fii ko men bonni, menen kadi men lamnditoytaake fii ko huuwoton"
  34,26,"Maaku: \"Joomi men renndinoyay en, refti O √±aawira hakkunde men goonga; Ko Kanko woni √ëaawoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  34,27,"Maaku: \"Hollee lam …óin …ói wa…ótidu-…óon e Makko kafidii…ói. Wanaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko Kanko woni Alla Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo On"
  34,28,"Men nuliraali ma, si wanaa e yim…ìe …ìen fow: wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa"
  34,29,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  34,30,"Maaku: \"Hino woodani on fodoore, nde o nennitantaake e mayre fotde saa'i, on ardintinantaake nde kadi"
  34,31,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'i: \"Men gom…óintaa ndee Alqur'aanaare muk, wanaa nden adiinde nde\". Sinno a tinayno tuma nde too√±u…ìe …ìen darnetee ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, hara yoga ma…ì…ìe no rutta yoga konngol, lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana townitinoo…ìe …ìen: \"Si wanaano onon nun, men wonayno gom…óim…ìe"
  34,32,"Townitinoo…ìe …ìen wi'ani lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen: \"E ko menen falinoo on e peewal …ìaawo ngal arde e mon? Si ko woni, on woniino bom…ìe"
  34,33,"Lo'inanoo…ìe …ìen kadi wi'ani townitinoo…ìe …ìen: \"Si ko woni, ko pewje (mon) jemma e √±alorma, tuma yamirayno…óon men yo men yeddu Alla, men wa…óana Mo fotondir…ói\". ∆Åe suu…ói ninse …óen, nde …ìe yi'unoo lepte …óen. Men wa…ói kolombooje e daa…óe …ìen yeddu…ìe. Hara …ìe yo…ìitete si wanaa ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon"
  34,34,"Men nulaali jertinoowo e yim…ìe saare, si wanaa neeminaa…ìe mayre …ìen wi'ay: \"Menen ko men yeddu…ìe ko nulida…óon kon"
  34,35,"∆Åe wi'i kadi: \"Ko menen …ìuri …óuu…óude jawle e …ìi…ì…ìe, men wonaali kadi leptetee…ìe"
  34,36,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyi, O …ìillini (mo O muuyi). Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa"
  34,37,"Wanaa jawle mon, wanaa jiidi mon woni ko …ìa…ótinirta on ka Amen …ìadal. Si wanaa …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e; …ìen …óon, hino woodani …ìe njo…ìdi sowaande, sabu ko …ìe golli kon, kam…ìe ka soorooji, ko …ìe hoolii…ìe"
  34,38,"∆Åen yaccotoo…ìe e ronkingol (yim…ìe …ìen) e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìen …óon, ka ka nder lepte woni ko …ìe tawnoytee"
  34,39,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O …ìillini mo (O muuyi e ma…ì…ìe). Kala non ko winti…óon e huunde, Kanko O lontinay nde. Ko Kanko woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Arsikoowo"
  34,40,"√ëalnde O moo…ìtindiroyta …ìe dendaangal, refti O daalana Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen: \"E ko …ìee …óoo (yim…ìe) rewaynoo on"
  34,41,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Senayee woodanii Ma! Ko An woni gi…óo amen gaanin ma…ì…ìe. Toode ko jinnaaji …óin …ìe rewaynoo, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, ko …óin (jinnaaji) gom…óini"
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Men wi'anoya …ìen too√±u…ìe: \"Mee…óee lepte Yiite nge fennayno…óon fii mun"
  34,43,"Si Aayeeje Amen …ìanngu…óe …óen janngaamma e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'a: \"Oo wonaali, si wanaa gorko faalaa…óo falagol on e ko baabiraa…ìe mon rewayno rewaynoo\". ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ndee (Alqur‚Äôaanaare) wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande\". Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'ani goonga kan nde ka arunoo e ma…ì…ìe: \"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  34,44,"Men addanaali …ìee, defte …óe …ìe janngata. Men mee…óaali nulude e ma…ì…ìe, jertinoowo ado maa"
  34,45,"Adinoo…ìe …ìe …ìen [kadi] fenniino (nulaa…ìe mun). [Yim…ìe maa …ìen] yottaaki sappa…ìal ko Men okkunoo …ìen kon. ∆Åen fenni Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, taskii no lepte Am …óen wa'unoo"
  34,46,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (huunde) wootere: \"Ko nde daroranton Alla …ói…óo …ói…óo e gooto gooto, refti miijito…óon. (Anndon) wondii…óo mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  34,47,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ìdi, …óum ko fii mon. Njo…ìdi am ndin wonaali, si wanaa ka Alla. Kanko Ko O Seedii…óo e kala huunde"
  34,48,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am ko werlortoo…óo [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga kan, timmin…óo anndugol wirnii…ói"
  34,49,"Maaku: \"Goonga kan arii [Iislaamu on], meere [keeferaaku] ngun alaa ka fee√±a, kadi, nde ruttotaako"
  34,50,"Maaku: \"Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko O Nanoowo, ∆Åadii…óo"
  34,51,"Sinno a tinayno, tuma nde …ìe …óenyii, - laaworde alanaa (…ìe), - …ìe nanngiree e nokkuure …ìadiinde"
  34,52,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii [Darngal] ngal\", e ko honno gom…óinal woonirani …ìe e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  34,53,"Hara non …ìe yeddiino nde ko adii, hi…ìe werlora ko wirnii e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko …ìe tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo ma…ì…ìe ko adii, tawde …ìe woniino e sikke cikkinii…óa"
  35,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Wa…óu…óo Malaa'ika'en nulaa…ìe, mar…ìe gabitanji(bibje) …ói …ói…ói, …ói tati e nayi. Himo …ìeyda ko O muuyi e tagu Makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yim…ìe …ìen, jogitotoo…óo nde alaa; kala kadi ko O jogitii, accitoowo …óum alaa …ìaawo (jogitagol) Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  35,3,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! jantee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko! E ko honno yiilirte…óon [e kaa goonga]"
  35,4,"Si …ìe fennii ma, pellet Nulaa…ìe (goo) fennanooma ado maa. Ko faade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  35,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! Anndee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata (seytaane) hodoowo on hodu on e fii Alla"
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko ga√±o wonani on. Haray jogitoree mo ga√±o. Anndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no …ìe jeydiree e yim…ìe dul…ìoowe ngen"
  35,7,"Hino woodani yeddu…ìe …ìen, lepte sa…ótu…óe. ∆Åeya gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hino woodani …ìe haforaneede e njo…ìdi mawndi"
  35,8,"E ko on cu…óinanaa…óo golle mun bon…óe, hara himo yi'a …óe mo∆¥∆¥u…óe? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna Mo O muuyi. Wata a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo ko …ìe woni huuwude"
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni wurtu…óo keneeli …óin, …ói sogga duule, Men yarnira …óum leydi yoorundi; Men wuurnitira …óum leydi ndin, …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non ummital ngal"
  35,10,"Kala taw…óo ko teddungal faalaa (yo o …óa…ì…ìir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fow: ko ka Makko woni ko konngol laa…ìungol ∆¥awata, golle mo∆¥∆¥e …óen …ìamta ngol. ∆Åen fewjoo…ìe boneeji, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe. Pewje …ìen …óen, ko bonay …óe"
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e to…ì…ìere (maniiyu), refti O wa…ói on nooneeji. Deyel saawataa, ngel lelnataa kadi, si wanaa e anndal Makko. Wuurnaa…óo wuurnetaake, …óuytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wanaa no e deftere. Pellet, …óum ko newanii …óum Alla"
  35,12,"Maaje …óen …ói…ói fotataa: [Ndiyam] goo …óoo …óam, ko wel…óam, laa…ìungo, newiingo njaram mun, ngoo …óaa, ko lan…óam haa…óu…óam. Hi…óon √±aama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hi…óon yaltina kadi hen, cu…óaari ndi …ìoornoto…óon. Hi…óa yi'a laa…óe …óen no awja e maggo, fii yo on …óa…ì…ìiron e …ìural Makko. Belajoo on yettay [Mo]"
  35,13,"Himo naada jemma on e der √±alorma on, O naada √±alorma on e nder jemma on. O elti kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On moo…óon woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko Kanko Laamu woodani. ∆äiya …ói noddoton gaanin Makko, …ói jeytaa yeru gorol tamara"
  35,14,"Si on noddu …ói, …ói nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si …ói nanoy, …ói jaabitotaako on. √ëalnde Darngal, …ói yeddoyay sirku mon on. Alaa habroowo ma, wano Humpitii…óo On"
  35,15,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, ko onon woni hatonjim…ìe e Alla …ìen, Alla kan, ko Kanko woni Galo Yettinii…óo On"
  35,16,"Si O yi…óii, O na…ìa on, O adda tagu hesu"
  35,17,∆äum wonaali sattu…óum ka Alla
  35,18,"Wonki ronndotaako do≈ãgal wonkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay huunde, hay si ko …ìadondiraa…óo Anndu ko jertintaa [nana waaju], ko …ìen huliroo…ìe Joomi mun ka wirnii, …ìe √±ii…ìi e Julde. Kala on la…ì…ìinii…óo, haray ko hoore makko o woni la…ì…ìinanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  35,19,Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa ni…ìe …óen e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa …óowdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuur…ìe …ìen fotata e maay…ìe …ìen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ìe ka genaale …ìen"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo fe∆¥∆¥ii e ma…ì…ìe"
  35,25,"Si …ìe fennii ma, hari adinoo…ìe …ìe …ìen fenniino (Nulaa…ìe mun), fewndo …ìen Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe addannoo …ìanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ìe …ìen (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An …óen wa…ótinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fu…óiniri …óam dim…óe seertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje seertyu…óe noone, e pete …ìaleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ìe …ìen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, ko anndu…ìe …ìen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"∆Åen janngoo…ìe Deftere Alla nden, …ìe √±ii…ìi e julde, …ìe nafqii ko Men arsiki …ìe kon gunndoo e kene, hi…ìe jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ìe njo…ìdiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, O …ìeyda …ìe e …ìural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa e Deftere nden, ko …óum woni goonga, gom…óinde e …óen won…óe yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko Humpitii…óo Rentu…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, …ìen …ìe Men su…ìii e jeyaa…ìe Amen. Hino e ma…ì…ìe too√±u…ìe hoore-mun, hino e ma…ì…ìe hakindin…óo, hino e ma…ì…ìe foolondiroo…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji, du≈ãayee Alla; ko …óum woni …ìural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …ói naatata e mun, hara hi…ìe cu…óiree ton, jawe ka≈ã≈ãe e kaalise e lu‚Äôu-lu‚Äôu; comci ma…ì…ìe …óin ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittan…óo en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, Warjotoo…óo"
  35,35,"On weernir…óo en …ìural Makko ngal, e galle √±ii…ìal, tampere (woo) he…ìataa en ton, wanaa ronkere he…ìata en ton"
  35,36,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani …ìen; maayde √±aawetaake e ma…ì…ìe, sakko …ìe maaya, …ìe hoynantaake kadi lepte magge …óen. Ko wano nii Men yo…ìitirta kala yeddu…óo"
  35,37,"Hara hi…ìe ooloo nder ton […ìe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla mo∆¥∆¥ere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo …ìe]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotoo…óo waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa mee…óee, sabu faabo alanaa too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko O Anndu…óo ko suu…óii e …ìer…óe"
  35,39,"Ko Kanko woni wa…óu…óo on lontii…ìe ka leydi. Kala yeddu…óo, ko e makko lorra geddi makko yantata. Yeddugol heefer…ìe …ìen, …ìeydataa …ìe ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa tikkere. Yeddugol …ìeydataa heefer…ìe …ìen, si wanaa hayrere"
  35,40,"Maaku: \"E on yi'ii rendii…ói mon rewoton gaanin Alla …óin? Hollee lam ko …ói tagi ka leydi. Kaa hi…ói mari ge…ìal e [tagugol] kammuuli …óin? Kaa Men addan …ìe Deftere, nde …ìe woni e …ìanndannduyee mun? Si ko woni, too√±oo…ìe …ìen alaa e fodude yoga ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa hodo"
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, fii wata …ói dirtu. Hay si …ói dirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako …ói e …ìaawo Makko. O laatike Mu√±√±ii…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,42,"∆Åe woodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje ma…ì…ìe, wonnde si jertinoowo arii e ma…ì…ìe, pellet, …ìe wonay …ìur…ìe feewude wootere e mofte …óen. Nde jertinoowo non arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, …óum …ìeydaali …ìe, si wanaa wo…ó…óitagol"
  35,43,"[∆Åe wa…óiri …óum] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje …ìen…óe. Pewje bon…óe …óen non huu…ìitataa, si wanaa jom-mun'en. Hara hi…ìe sabbitii, si wanaa sunna (Alla) on e adinoo…ìe …ìen? A he…ìantaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a he…ìantaa sunna Alla waylir…óum"
  35,44,"E …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ìe taskoo ko honno battane adinoo…ìe …ìen wonirnoo? Hari no …ìuri …ìe tii…óude doole. Alla siforaali wonnde go…ó…óum no ronkina Mo ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O Anndu…óo, Hattan…óo"
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yim…ìe …ìen ko …ìe faggitorii kon, O accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana …ìe haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal ma…ì…ìe ngal hewtii, [O nanngay …ìe], tawde pellet, Alla ko Reenu…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  36,1,Yaa-Siin
  36,2,Mi woondirii Al*ur'aana √±e√±aande nden
  36,3,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  36,4,E dow laawol focciingol
  36,5,"Jippinannde On Foolu…óo, Hinnotoo"
  36,6,"Fii yo a jertinir nde yim…ìe, …ìe baabiraa…ìe mun jertinanooka: …ìen ko welsindii…ìe"
  36,7,"Gom…óii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe; …ìen …óon gom…óintaa"
  36,8,"Menen Men wa…óii ka daa…óe ma…ì…ìe kolommbooje, …óen ko yottii…óe ka bokku…óe; hara ko …ìe ≈ãallinii…ìe"
  36,9,"Men wa…ói yeeso ma…ì…ìe heedo, …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe kadi heedo, Men hippi …ìe (gite …óen); wa…óti …ìe yi'ataa [goonga]"
  36,10,"Hino fota e ma…ì…ìe, foti a jertini …ìe, maa a jertinaali …ìe; …ìe gom…óintaa"
  36,11,"Anndu ko jertintaa (ja…ìa), ko on jokku…óo Jantoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o huli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo haforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi"
  36,12,"Ko Menen woni wuurnitoo…ìe maay…ìe …ìen, Men winnda ko …ìe ardini e batteeji ma…ì…ìe. Kala huunde, Me…óen mofti nde e deftere …ìanngunde"
  36,13,"Piyan-…ìe misal, fii yim…ìe saare, tuma nde Nulaa…ìe arunoo …ìe"
  36,14,"Nde Men nulunoo e ma…ì…ìe, [Nulaa…ìe] …ói…óo, …ìe fenni …ìen, Men sammbiniri …ìen, tata…ìo, …ìe wi'i: \"Menen, ko men Nulaa…ìe e mo'on"
  36,15,"[Yim…ìe saare nden] wi'i: \"On wonaali, si wanaa ko on …ìanndinke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaali hay huunde, on wonaali, si wanaa ko on fenoo…ìe"
  36,16,"[Nulaa…ìe …ìen] wi'i: \"Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko men Nulaa…ìe e mo'on"
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wanaa yottingol …ìanngina"
  36,18,"[Yim…ìe saare nden] wi'iti: \"Men hiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on ha…óitaaki, ma men fi…óu on, lepte muusu…óe kadi memira on immorde e amen"
  36,19,"[Nulaa…ìe …ìen kadi] wi'iti: \"Kiite mon …óin, hi…óon wonndi e mun. Ko si on waajaama (hiitino…óon)? Tigi on, ko on yim…ìe fantinoo…ìe"
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ìuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, o ari himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, kori jokkee Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  36,21,"jokkee …ìen …ìe lamndotaako on njo…ìdi, …ìen ko fewnaa…ìe"
  36,22,E ko ha…óata lam rewugol On tagu…óo Lam? Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto rewetee…ói gaanin Makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii lam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali lam hay huunde, …ói d…óandataa lam kadi"
  36,24,"Haray min ontuma, mi wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  36,25,"Min on, mi gom…óinii Joomi mon, nananee lam"
  36,26,"wi'anaa: \"Naatu Aljanna\". O wi'i: \"Haaniino yim…ìe am …ìen annda"
  36,27,"ko Joomi am haforani lam, O wa…ói lam e teddinaa…ìe …ìen"
  36,28,"Men jippiniraano koneeli ka kammu, e yim…ìe makko …ìen, …ìaawo maako. Men wonaanii jippinoo…ìe […óin koneeli]"
  36,29,"(Halkeede ma…ì…ìe) wonaali, si wanaa haacaango wooto, tawi …ìe laatii maay…ìe-…ìutti"
  36,30,"Ee hayreede jeyaa…ìe [fenunoo…ìe]! Nulaa…óo araali e …ì…ìe, si wanaa …ìe wa…ótayno mo jalnori"
  36,31,E …ìee yi'aali …óuu…óii e gire …óe Men halki ado ma…ì…ìe? Wonnde …ìen ruttitotaako e ma…ì…ìe
  36,32,"∆Åe fow wonaali, si wanaa ko moo…ìoytee…ìe ka Amen"
  36,33,"Hino wonani …ìe maande: leydi yoorundi ndin, Men wuurniti ndi, Men yaltini gabbe e mayri, tawi ko e …óen …ìe √±aamata"
  36,34,"Men wa…ói e mayri gese tamarooje e inabuuje, Men …ìulni e mayri …ìulli(ceewle)"
  36,35,fii no …ìe √±aamira dim…óe mun …óen e kon ko …ìe golliri juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen. E …ìe yettataa (Alla)
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii tagu…óo nooneeji …óin On fow: gila e ko leydi ndin fu…óinta kon, haa e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, e kon ko …ìe anndaa"
  36,37,"Maande goo kadi wonanii …ìe: e jemma on, Me…óen sorta e makko √±alorma on, tawa …ìe wontii e niwre"
  36,38,"E naange ngen, hinge doga haa e √±ii…ìirde magge; …óum ko e…ì…ìoore Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On"
  36,39,"E lewru ndun, Men e…ì…ìani ndu jipporde, haa ndu wa…ótinira wa baa≈ãal tamaro kii…óngal"
  36,40,"Wanaa naange ngen woni ko haanini hewtitagol lewru ndun, wanaa jemma on woni ko aditotoo √±alorma on; kala majji non, ko e laawol mun woni dogude"
  36,41,"Maande goo wonanii …ìe, wonnde Men roondike geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol, ka laana hebbinaaka"
  36,42,"Men tagani …ìe sugu makko, ko …ìe wa…ó…óoo"
  36,43,"Si Me…óen yi…óuno, Men yoolayno …ìe; hara faabo alanaa …ìe, wanaa kadi …ìe da…óndetee…ìe"
  36,44,"si wanaa yurmeende immornde e Amen, e dakmitagol haa e saanga"
  36,45,"Si …ìe wi'anaama: \"Rentee e kon ko woni yeeso mon e …ìaawo mon, belajo'o, on yurminte"
  36,46,"Aaya woo e Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen araali e ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa …ìe …óuurnoo…óe"
  36,47,"Si …ìe wi'anaama kadi: \"Wintee(nafqe) e kon Alla arsiki on\", yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'ana gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"E men √±amminay on taw…óo si Alla muuyuno, O √±amminayno mo? On wonaali, si wanaa e nder majjere …ìanngunde"
  36,48,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  36,49,"∆Åe habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango wooto, nanngayngo …ìe, hara hi…ìe yeddondira"
  36,50,"∆Åe waawoytaa wasiyagol ontuma, wanaa …ìe ruttoytoo…ìe e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen"
  36,51,"Wutte ka Alaandu, …ìe yaltira e genaale …óen, …ìe he√±ora ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe"
  36,52,"hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ee bone amen! Ko hommbo immini men e genaale amen?\" Ko …óum woni ko Hinaranke On fodunoo; Nulaa…ìe …ìen goonginii"
  36,53,"(Ummital) ngal wonaano, si wanaa haacaango gooto, tawi …ìe fow …ìe addaama ka Amen"
  36,54,"Hannde non, wonkii too√±irtaake hay huunde. On yo…ìitirtaake, si wanaa kon ko gollayno…óon"
  36,55,"Yim…ìe Aljanna …ìe hannde, pellet, hi…ìe e nder soklio, hi…ìe neeminoo"
  36,56,"kam…ìe e genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen,e ley …óow…óe, hi…ìe so…ì…ìindii e hoore dan…óe"
  36,57,"Hino woodani …ìe ton, …ìi…ó…ìe le…ó…óe, hino woodani kadi, kon ko …ìe noddata"
  36,58,"Salaamun\", konngol [kisiyee], immorde e Joomiraa…óo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  36,59,"Sertee non hande, onon …ìee bom…ìe"
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mon, onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama, wonnde wata on rewu seytaane? Tawde pellet, ko o ga√±o mon …ìanngu…óo"
  36,61,"[Mi yamiri on] kadi rewugol Lam. Ko ngol woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  36,62,Gom…óii o majjinii tagu …óuu…óungu e mon. E on wonaano haqqiloo…ìe
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge wonano…óon fodaneede ngen"
  36,64,"Naatiree nge hannde, sabu kon ko yeddirayno…óon"
  36,65,"Hannde, Men notay e kunndule ma…ì…ìe …óen, juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yewta Men, koy…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen kadi seeditoo e kon ko …ìe wonunoo e faggitagol"
  36,66,"Si Men yi…óuno, Men mehayno gite ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe adondira e laawol ngol. Kono ko honno …ìe yiirata"
